o 小北/阿码/老潘 each appear at least 2 times?\n- Summary: Is the summary narrative (not bullet list)?\n\n**Output format:**\nReturn:\n1. Four scores (1-5 each) with explanations\n2. Total score (sum /20)\n3. Blocking items (any dimension ≤ 2)\n4. Suggestions for improvement\n\n**Important**: This is a READ-ONLY review. Do NOT modify any files. Just return your findings as a message.","subagent_type":"student-qa"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5071dd61-4cb8-490e-a97a-6edea443d84b","uuid":"6501c1e2-7704-4411-aa9f-fe1f4b732b26"}
