{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_2a3740ee9497464d9001358d","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→/*\n     2→ * 示例：测试生命周期 - 使用 @BeforeEach 消除重复代码。\n     3→ * 运行方式：mvn -q -f chapters/week_06/starter_code/pom.xml test -Dtest=LibraryTrackerLifecycleTest\n     4→ * 预期输出：测试通过，每个测试方法前都会执行 setUp()\n     5→ *\n     6→ * 关键概念：\n     7→ * - @BeforeEach: 每个测试方法执行前运行\n     8→ * - @AfterEach: 每个测试方法执行后运行（本例未展示）\n     9→ * - 测试隔离：每个测试都应该从干净状态开始\n    10→ */\n    11→\n    12→import org.junit.jupiter.api.BeforeEach;\n    13→import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n    14→import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.*;\n    15→\n    16→/**\n    17→ * 图书类\n    18→ */\n    19→class Book {\n    20→    private String title;\n    21→    private String author;\n    22→    private String isbn;\n    23→\n    24→    public Book(String title, String author, String isbn) {\n    25→        this.title = title;\n    26→        this.author = author;\n    27→        this.isbn = isbn;\n    28→    }\n    29→\n    30→    public String getTitle() { return title; }\n    31→    public String getAuthor() { return author; }\n    32→    public String getIsbn() { return isbn; }\n    33→}\n    34→\n    35→/**\n    36→ * 借阅记录类\n    37→ */\n    38→class BorrowRecord {\n    39→    private String isbn;\n    40→    private String borrower;\n    41→\n    42→    public BorrowRecord(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    43→        this.isbn = isbn;\n    44→        this.borrower = borrower;\n    45→    }\n    46→\n    47→    public String getIsbn() { return isbn; }\n    48→    public String getBorrower() { return borrower; }\n    49→}\n    50→\n    51→/**\n    52→ * 图书追踪器\n    53→ */\n    54→class LibraryTracker {\n    55→    private java.util.HashMap<String, Book> booksByIsbn;\n    56→    private java.util.ArrayList<BorrowRecord> borrowRecords;\n    57→\n    58→    public LibraryTracker() {\n    59→        booksByIsbn = new java.util.HashMap<>();\n    60→        borrowRecords = new java.util.ArrayList<>();\n    61→    }\n    62→\n    63→    public void addBook(Book book) {\n    64→        if (book == null || book.getIsbn() == null) {\n    65→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书信息不完整\");\n    66→        }\n    67→        booksByIsbn.put(book.getIsbn(), book);\n    68→    }\n    69→\n    70→    public Book findBook(String isbn) {\n    71→        return booksByIsbn.get(isbn);\n    72→    }\n    73→\n    74→    public java.util.List<Book> listAllBooks() {\n    75→        return new java.util.ArrayList<>(booksByIsbn.values());\n    76→    }\n    77→\n    78→    public void removeBook(String isbn) {\n    79→        booksByIsbn.remove(isbn);\n    80→    }\n    81→\n    82→    public void borrowBook(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    83→        if (isbn == null || isbn.isEmpty()) {\n    84→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"ISBN 不能为空\");\n    85→        }\n    86→        if (borrower == null || borrower.isEmpty()) {\n    87→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"借阅人不能为空\");\n    88→        }\n    89→        if (!booksByIsbn.containsKey(isbn)) {\n    90→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书不存在：\" + isbn);\n    91→        }\n    92→        borrowRecords.add(new BorrowRecord(isbn, borrower));\n    93→    }\n    94→\n    95→    public void returnBook(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    96→        java.util.Iterator<BorrowRecord> it = borrowRecords.iterator();\n    97→        while (it.hasNext()) {\n    98→            BorrowRecord record = it.next();\n    99→            if (record.getIsbn().equals(isbn) && record.getBorrower().equals(borrower)) {\n   100→                it.remove();\n   101→                return;\n   102→            }\n   103→        }\n   104→        throw new IllegalStateException(\"未找到对应的借阅记录\");\n   105→    }\n   106→\n   107→    public boolean hasBorrowRecord(String isbn, String borrower) {\n   108→        for (BorrowRecord record : borrowRecords) {\n   109→            if (record.getIsbn().equals(isbn) && record.getBorrower().equals(borrower)) {\n   110→                return true;\n   111→            }\n   112→        }\n   113→        return false;\n   114→    }\n   115→}\n   116→\n   117→/**\n   118→ * 展示测试生命周期的测试类\n   119→ *\n   120→ * 反例（不使用 @BeforeEach 时的重复代码）：\n   121→ * ```java\n   122→ * @Test\n   123→ * void test1() {\n   124→ *     LibraryTracker tracker = new LibraryTracker();  // 重复\n   125→ *     Book testBook = new Book(\"测试书\", \"作者\", \"TEST-ISBN\");  // 重复\n   126→ *     // ... 测试逻辑\n   127→ * }\n   128→ *\n   129→ * @Test\n   130→ * void test2() {\n   131→ *     LibraryTracker tracker = new LibraryTracker();  // 重复\n   132→ *     Book testBook = new Book(\"测试书\", \"作者\", \"TEST-ISBN\");  // 重复\n   133→ *     // ... 测试逻辑\n   134→ * }\n   135→ * ```\n   136→ */\n   137→class LibraryTrackerLifecycleTest {\n   138→\n   139→    // 实例变量，在 setUp() 中初始化\n   140→    private LibraryTracker tracker;\n   141→    private Book testBook;\n   142→\n   143→    /**\n   144→     * @BeforeEach 标记的方法会在每个 @Test 方法执行前运行。\n   145→     * 这确保了每个测试都从一个干净、一致的状态开始。\n   146→     *\n   147→     * 为什么重要？\n   148→     * - 测试隔离：一个测试的失败不应该影响其他测试\n   149→     * - 可重复性：无论单独运行还是批量运行，结果都一致\n   150→     * - DRY 原则：避免在每个测试方法中重复初始化代码\n   151→     */\n   152→    @BeforeEach\n   153→    void setUp() {\n   154→        // 每个测试方法前都会执行\n   155→        tracker = new LibraryTracker();\n   156→        testBook = new Book(\"测试书\", \"测试作者\", \"TEST-ISBN\");\n   157→    }\n   158→\n   159→    @Test\n   160→    void shouldAddBook() {\n   161→        // 直接使用 setUp() 创建的 tracker 和 testBook\n   162→        tracker.addBook(testBook);\n   163→        assertNotNull(tracker.findBook(\"TEST-ISBN\"));\n   164→    }\n   165→\n   166→    @Test\n   167→    void shouldBorrowBook() {\n   168→        // 借阅流程测试\n   169→        tracker.addBook(testBook);\n   170→        tracker.borrowBook(\"TEST-ISBN\", \"小北\");\n   171→\n   172→        // 验证借阅记录存在\n   173→        assertTrue(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"TEST-ISBN\", \"小北\"));\n   174→    }\n   175→\n   176→    @Test\n   177→    void shouldReturnBook() {\n   178→        // 归还流程测试\n   179→        tracker.addBook(testBook);\n   180→        tracker.borrowBook(\"TEST-ISBN\", \"小北\");\n   181→        tracker.returnBook(\"TEST-ISBN\", \"小北\");\n   182→\n   183→        // 验证借阅记录已清除\n   184→        assertFalse(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"TEST-ISBN\", \"小北\"));\n   185→    }\n   186→\n   187→    @Test\n   188→    void shouldListAllBooks() {\n   189→        tracker.addBook(testBook);\n   190→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书2\", \"作者B\", \"ISBN-2\"));\n   191→\n   192→        var books = tracker.listAllBooks();\n   193→\n   194→        assertEquals(2, books.size());\n   195→    }\n   196→\n   197→    @Test\n   198→    void shouldRemoveBook() {\n   199→        tracker.addBook(testBook);\n   200→        assertNotNull(tracker.findBook(\"TEST-ISBN\"));\n   201→\n   202→        tracker.removeBook(\"TEST-ISBN\");\n   203→\n   204→        assertNull(tracker.findBook(\"TEST-ISBN\"));\n   205→    }\n   206→\n   207→    /**\n   208→     * @AfterEach 示例（如果需要清理资源）\n   209→     *\n   210→     * @AfterEach\n   211→     * void tearDown() {\n   212→     *     // 清理临时文件、关闭数据库连接等\n   213→     *     // 对于内存存储，通常不需要显式清理\n   214→     * }\n   215→     */\n   216→}\n   217→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_14f9c3afc6df478fbe525d70","session_id":"5071dd61-4cb8-490e-a97a-6edea443d84b","uuid":"4a11186a-02ca-4c7d-90f2-9fdb6137bf5f"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_bdd5eadc8239434199bb08f0","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→/*\n     2→ * 示例：手动验证的困境——展示为什么需要自动化测试。\n     3→ * 运行方式：javac 01_manual_testing_pain.java && java ManualTestingPainDemo\n     4→ * 预期输出：程序运行正常，但借书功能实际上有 bug（未正确验证图书是否存在）\n     5→ */\n     6→\n     7→/**\n     8→ * 图书类 - 来自 Week 05\n     9→ */\n    10→class Book {\n    11→    private String title;\n    12→    private String author;\n    13→    private String isbn;\n    14→\n    15→    public Book(String title, String author, String isbn) {\n    16→        this.title = title;\n    17→        this.author = author;\n    18→        this.isbn = isbn;\n    19→    }\n    20→\n    21→    public String getTitle() { return title; }\n    22→    public String getAuthor() { return author; }\n    23→    public String getIsbn() { return isbn; }\n    24→}\n    25→\n    26→/**\n    27→ * 有 bug 的图书追踪器 - 模拟小北改代码后破坏功能的情况\n    28→ */\n    29→class LibraryTrackerWithBug {\n    30→    private java.util.HashMap<String, Book> booksByIsbn;\n    31→    private java.util.ArrayList<BorrowRecord> borrowRecords;\n    32→\n    33→    public LibraryTrackerWithBug() {\n    34→        booksByIsbn = new java.util.HashMap<>();\n    35→        borrowRecords = new java.util.ArrayList<>();\n    36→    }\n    37→\n    38→    public void addBook(Book book) {\n    39→        if (book == null || book.getIsbn() == null) {\n    40→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书信息不完整\");\n    41→        }\n    42→        booksByIsbn.put(book.getIsbn(), book);\n    43→    }\n    44→\n    45→    // 小北重构了这个方法，返回 Optional，但忘记同步修改 borrowBook\n    46→    public java.util.Optional<Book> findBook(String isbn) {\n    47→        return java.util.Optional.ofNullable(booksByIsbn.get(isbn));\n    48→    }\n    49→\n    50→    // BUG: 这个方法没有更新，仍然按旧逻辑处理\n    51→    public void borrowBook(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    52→        if (isbn == null || isbn.isEmpty()) {\n    53→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"ISBN 不能为空\");\n    54→        }\n    55→\n    56→        // BUG: 小北忘了这里需要调整！findBook 现在返回 Optional\n    57→        // 但代码仍然直接判断，导致逻辑错误\n    58→        Book book = findBook(isbn).orElse(null);\n    59→\n    60→        // 这个检查本应该阻止借阅不存在的书，但由于上面的问题...\n    61→        if (book == null) {\n    62→            // 实际上这里应该抛异常，但小北在重构时注释掉了\n    63→            // throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书不存在：\" + isbn);\n    64→            System.out.println(\"警告：图书不存在，但继续执行...\");\n    65→        }\n    66→\n    67→        // BUG: 即使书不存在，也会创建借阅记录！\n    68→        borrowRecords.add(new BorrowRecord(isbn, borrower));\n    69→        System.out.println(\"借阅成功：\" + borrower + \" 借走了 ISBN:\" + isbn);\n    70→    }\n    71→\n    72→    public boolean hasBorrowRecord(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    73→        for (BorrowRecord record : borrowRecords) {\n    74→            if (record.getIsbn().equals(isbn) && record.getBorrower().equals(borrower)) {\n    75→                return true;\n    76→            }\n    77→        }\n    78→        return false;\n    79→    }\n    80→}\n    81→\n    82→/**\n    83→ * 借阅记录类\n    84→ */\n    85→class BorrowRecord {\n    86→    private String isbn;\n    87→    private String borrower;\n    88→\n    89→    public BorrowRecord(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    90→        this.isbn = isbn;\n    91→        this.borrower = borrower;\n    92→    }\n    93→\n    94→    public String getIsbn() { return isbn; }\n    95→    public String getBorrower() { return borrower; }\n    96→}\n    97→\n    98→/**\n    99→ * 手动验证的主程序 - 只能测试小北\"想到\"的场景\n   100→ */\n   101→class ManualTestingPainDemo {\n   102→    public static void main(String[] args) {\n   103→        LibraryTrackerWithBug tracker = new LibraryTrackerWithBug();\n   104→\n   105→        // 小北手动测试：添加一本书，然后借阅它\n   106→        System.out.println(\"=== 手动测试场景1：正常借阅 ===\");\n   107→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"Java 核心技术\", \"Cay Horstmann\", \"978-111\"));\n   108→        tracker.borrowBook(\"978-111\", \"小北\");\n   109→        System.out.println(\"借阅记录存在: \" + tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"978-111\", \"小北\"));\n   110→\n   111→        // 小北手动测试：查询功能\n   112→        System.out.println(\"\\n=== 手动测试场景2：查询图书 ===\");\n   113→        var book = tracker.findBook(\"978-111\");\n   114→        System.out.println(\"找到图书: \" + book.isPresent());\n   115→\n   116→        // 小北忘了测试这个场景：借阅不存在的书！\n   117→        System.out.println(\"\\n=== 遗漏的测试场景：借阅不存在的书 ===\");\n   118→        System.out.println(\"（小北忘了测试这个边界情况）\");\n   119→        tracker.borrowBook(\"不存在的ISBN\", \"阿码\");\n   120→        System.out.println(\"借阅记录存在: \" + tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"不存在的ISBN\", \"阿码\"));\n   121→        System.out.println(\"BUG: 不存在的书也被借走了！\");\n   122→\n   123→        System.out.println(\"\\n=== 问题总结 ===\");\n   124→        System.out.println(\"手动验证的问题：\");\n   125→        System.out.println(\"1. 只能覆盖'想到'的场景，容易遗漏边界情况\");\n   126→        System.out.println(\"2. 每次改代码后都要重新手动验证所有功能\");\n   127→        System.out.println(\"3. 无法自动化执行，容易因疏忽而遗漏\");\n   128→        System.out.println(\"4. 重构时如果没有测试守护，很容易引入 bug\");\n   129→    }\n   130→}\n   131→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_14f9c3afc6df478fbe525d70","session_id":"5071dd61-4cb8-490e-a97a-6edea443d84b","uuid":"6a7024ba-9321-44e4-8a99-6b7a9b8c665e"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_9cf96d97a9bc4cdcaf066c28","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→/*\n     2→ * 示例：异常测试 - 使用 assertThrows 验证防御式编程。\n     3→ * 运行方式：mvn -q -f chapters/week_06/starter_code/pom.xml test -Dtest=LibraryTrackerExceptionTest\n     4→ * 预期输出：测试通过，所有异常场景都被正确捕获\n     5→ *\n     6→ * 关键概念：\n     7→ * - assertThrows: 验证代码是否抛出指定异常\n     8→ * - Lambda 表达式: 将待测代码包装为可执行块\n     9→ * - 异常消息验证: 确保异常信息准确\n    10→ *\n    11→ * 回顾桥：Week 03 学习的防御式编程，现在用测试来验证\n    12→ */\n    13→\n    14→import org.junit.jupiter.api.BeforeEach;\n    15→import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n    16→import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.*;\n    17→\n    18→/**\n    19→ * 图书类\n    20→ */\n    21→class Book {\n    22→    private String title;\n    23→    private String author;\n    24→    private String isbn;\n    25→\n    26→    public Book(String title, String author, String isbn) {\n    27→        this.title = title;\n    28→        this.author = author;\n    29→        this.isbn = isbn;\n    30→    }\n    31→\n    32→    public String getTitle() { return title; }\n    33→    public String getAuthor() { return author; }\n    34→    public String getIsbn() { return isbn; }\n    35→}\n    36→\n    37→/**\n    38→ * 借阅记录类\n    39→ */\n    40→class BorrowRecord {\n    41→    private String isbn;\n    42→    private String borrower;\n    43→\n    44→    public BorrowRecord(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    45→        this.isbn = isbn;\n    46→        this.borrower = borrower;\n    47→    }\n    48→\n    49→    public String getIsbn() { return isbn; }\n    50→    public String getBorrower() { return borrower; }\n    51→}\n    52→\n    53→/**\n    54→ * 带防御式编程的图书追踪器\n    55→ */\n    56→class LibraryTracker {\n    57→    private java.util.HashMap<String, Book> booksByIsbn;\n    58→    private java.util.ArrayList<BorrowRecord> borrowRecords;\n    59→\n    60→    public LibraryTracker() {\n    61→        booksByIsbn = new java.util.HashMap<>();\n    62→        borrowRecords = new java.util.ArrayList<>();\n    63→    }\n    64→\n    65→    public void addBook(Book book) {\n    66→        // 防御式编程：参数校验\n    67→        if (book == null) {\n    68→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书不能为空\");\n    69→        }\n    70→        if (book.getIsbn() == null || book.getIsbn().isEmpty()) {\n    71→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"ISBN 不能为空\");\n    72→        }\n    73→        booksByIsbn.put(book.getIsbn(), book);\n    74→    }\n    75→\n    76→    public Book findBook(String isbn) {\n    77→        return booksByIsbn.get(isbn);\n    78→    }\n    79→\n    80→    public void borrowBook(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    81→        // 防御式编程：多层参数校验\n    82→        if (isbn == null || isbn.isEmpty()) {\n    83→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"ISBN 不能为空\");\n    84→        }\n    85→        if (borrower == null || borrower.isEmpty()) {\n    86→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"借阅人不能为空\");\n    87→        }\n    88→        if (!booksByIsbn.containsKey(isbn)) {\n    89→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书不存在：\" + isbn);\n    90→        }\n    91→        borrowRecords.add(new BorrowRecord(isbn, borrower));\n    92→    }\n    93→\n    94→    public boolean hasBorrowRecord(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    95→        for (BorrowRecord record : borrowRecords) {\n    96→            if (record.getIsbn().equals(isbn) && record.getBorrower().equals(borrower)) {\n    97→                return true;\n    98→            }\n    99→        }\n   100→        return false;\n   101→    }\n   102→}\n   103→\n   104→/**\n   105→ * 异常测试类\n   106→ *\n   107→ * 反例（错误的异常测试写法）：\n   108→ * ```java\n   109→ * @Test\n   110→ * void badTest() {\n   111→ *     try {\n   112→ *         tracker.borrowBook(null, \"小北\");\n   113→ *         fail(\"应该抛出异常\");  // 容易忘记写这行\n   114→ *     } catch (IllegalArgumentException e) {\n   115→ *         // 测试通过\n   116→ *     }\n   117→ * }\n   118→ * ```\n   119→ *\n   120→ * 上面的写法容易出错，JUnit 5 提供了 assertThrows 来简化：\n   121→ */\n   122→class LibraryTrackerExceptionTest {\n   123→\n   124→    private LibraryTracker tracker;\n   125→\n   126→    @BeforeEach\n   127→    void setUp() {\n   128→        tracker = new LibraryTracker();\n   129→    }\n   130→\n   131→    @Test\n   132→    void shouldThrowExceptionWhenBorrowingWithNullIsbn() {\n   133→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   134→\n   135→        // assertThrows 接收两个参数：\n   136→        // 1. 期望的异常类型（Class 对象）\n   137→        // 2. 待执行的代码（Lambda 表达式）\n   138→        Exception exception = assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   139→            tracker.borrowBook(null, \"小北\");\n   140→        });\n   141→\n   142→        // 还可以验证异常消息\n   143→        assertEquals(\"ISBN 不能为空\", exception.getMessage());\n   144→    }\n   145→\n   146→    @Test\n   147→    void shouldThrowExceptionWhenBorrowingWithEmptyIsbn() {\n   148→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   149→\n   150→        Exception exception = assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   151→            tracker.borrowBook(\"\", \"小北\");\n   152→        });\n   153→\n   154→        assertEquals(\"ISBN 不能为空\", exception.getMessage());\n   155→    }\n   156→\n   157→    @Test\n   158→    void shouldThrowExceptionWhenBorrowingNonExistentBook() {\n   159→        // 尝试借阅不存在的书\n   160→        Exception exception = assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   161→            tracker.borrowBook(\"不存在的ISBN\", \"小北\");\n   162→        });\n   163→\n   164→        // 使用 contains 验证消息包含特定内容（不要求完全匹配）\n   165→        assertTrue(exception.getMessage().contains(\"图书不存在\"));\n   166→    }\n   167→\n   168→    @Test\n   169→    void shouldThrowExceptionWhenBorrowerIsNull() {\n   170→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   171→\n   172→        Exception exception = assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   173→            tracker.borrowBook(\"ISBN-1\", null);\n   174→        });\n   175→\n   176→        assertEquals(\"借阅人不能为空\", exception.getMessage());\n   177→    }\n   178→\n   179→    @Test\n   180→    void shouldThrowExceptionWhenAddingNullBook() {\n   181→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   182→            tracker.addBook(null);\n   183→        });\n   184→    }\n   185→\n   186→    @Test\n   187→    void shouldThrowExceptionWhenAddingBookWithNullIsbn() {\n   188→        Book bookWithNullIsbn = new Book(\"书\", \"作者\", null);\n   189→\n   190→        Exception exception = assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   191→            tracker.addBook(bookWithNullIsbn);\n   192→        });\n   193→\n   194→        assertEquals(\"ISBN 不能为空\", exception.getMessage());\n   195→    }\n   196→\n   197→    /**\n   198→     * assertThrows 的返回值是抛出的异常对象，可以进一步验证：\n   199→     * - 异常消息\n   200→     * - 异常原因（cause）\n   201→     * - 异常类型（如果是自定义异常）\n   202→     */\n   203→    @Test\n   204→    void shouldPreserveExceptionDetails() {\n   205→        IllegalArgumentException exception = assertThrows(\n   206→            IllegalArgumentException.class,\n   207→            () -> tracker.borrowBook(\"未知ISBN\", \"小北\")\n   208→        );\n   209→\n   210→        // 验证异常消息包含 ISBN 信息\n   211→        String message = exception.getMessage();\n   212→        assertNotNull(message);\n   213→        assertTrue(message.contains(\"未知ISBN\"), \"异常消息应该包含 ISBN 信息\");\n   214→    }\n   215→}\n   216→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_14f9c3afc6df478fbe525d70","session_id":"5071dd61-4cb8-490e-a97a-6edea443d84b","uuid":"533613c1-8662-4735-8de6-713d15428bc8"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_854c14d2fd11447b8175a5b2","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→/*\n     2→ * 示例：CampusFlow Repository 层单元测试。\n     3→ * 运行方式：mvn -q -f chapters/week_06/starter_code/pom.xml test -Dtest=CampusFlowRepositoryTest\n     4→ * 预期输出：测试通过，核心方法覆盖率 80%+\n     5→ *\n     6→ * 本周 CampusFlow 推进：\n     7→ * - 上周状态：使用 ArrayList/HashMap 重构了数据存储层，Repository 模式落地\n     8→ * - 本周改进：为 Repository 层添加单元测试，确保核心增删改查方法有测试覆盖\n     9→ * - 目标：核心方法（save/findById/findAll/delete）测试覆盖率 80%+\n    10→ *\n    11→ * 涉及的本周概念：\n    12→ * - JUnit 5 基础（@Test, 断言方法）\n    13→ * - 测试生命周期（@BeforeEach）\n    14→ * - 异常测试（assertThrows）\n    15→ * - 参数化测试（@ParameterizedTest, @CsvSource）\n    16→ */\n    17→\n    18→import org.junit.jupiter.api.BeforeEach;\n    19→import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n    20→import org.junit.jupiter.params.ParameterizedTest;\n    21→import org.junit.jupiter.params.provider.CsvSource;\n    22→import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.*;\n    23→\n    24→/**\n    25→ * Task 实体类 - CampusFlow 的核心领域对象\n    26→ * 对应 Week 05 的 TaskRepository 中的 Task\n    27→ */\n    28→class Task {\n    29→    private String id;\n    30→    private String title;\n    31→    private String status;\n    32→    private String assignee;\n    33→\n    34→    public Task(String id, String title, String status) {\n    35→        this.id = id;\n    36→        this.title = title;\n    37→        this.status = status;\n    38→    }\n    39→\n    40→    public Task(String id, String title, String status, String assignee) {\n    41→        this(id, title, status);\n    42→        this.assignee = assignee;\n    43→    }\n    44→\n    45→    public String getId() { return id; }\n    46→    public String getTitle() { return title; }\n    47→    public String getStatus() { return status; }\n    48→    public String getAssignee() { return assignee; }\n    49→\n    50→    public void setTitle(String title) { this.title = title; }\n    51→    public void setStatus(String status) { this.status = status; }\n    52→    public void setAssignee(String assignee) { this.assignee = assignee; }\n    53→}\n    54→\n    55→/**\n    56→ * TaskRepository - CampusFlow 的任务仓储层\n    57→ * 基于 Week 05 的实现，使用 HashMap + ArrayList 组合\n    58→ */\n    59→class TaskRepository {\n    60→    private final java.util.HashMap<String, Task> tasksById;\n    61→    private final java.util.ArrayList<Task> taskList;\n    62→\n    63→    public TaskRepository() {\n    64→        this.tasksById = new java.util.HashMap<>();\n    65→        this.taskList = new java.util.ArrayList<>();\n    66→    }\n    67→\n    68→    /**\n    69→     * 保存任务（新增或更新）\n    70→     */\n    71→    public void save(Task task) {\n    72→        if (task == null) {\n    73→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"Task 不能为空\");\n    74→        }\n    75→        if (task.getId() == null || task.getId().isEmpty()) {\n    76→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"Task ID 不能为空\");\n    77→        }\n    78→\n    79→        tasksById.put(task.getId(), task);\n    80→\n    81→        // 如果列表中已存在，先删除旧引用\n    82→        taskList.removeIf(t -> t.getId().equals(task.getId()));\n    83→        taskList.add(task);\n    84→    }\n    85→\n    86→    /**\n    87→     * 根据 ID 查找任务\n    88→     */\n    89→    public java.util.Optional<Task> findById(String id) {\n    90→        return java.util.Optional.ofNullable(tasksById.get(id));\n    91→    }\n    92→\n    93→    /**\n    94→     * 获取所有任务\n    95→     */\n    96→    public java.util.List<Task> findAll() {\n    97→        return new java.util.ArrayList<>(taskList);\n    98→    }\n    99→\n   100→    /**\n   101→     * 根据状态查找任务\n   102→     */\n   103→    public java.util.List<Task> findByStatus(String status) {\n   104→        return taskList.stream()\n   105→            .filter(t -> t.getStatus().equals(status))\n   106→            .collect(java.util.stream.Collectors.toList());\n   107→    }\n   108→\n   109→    /**\n   110→     * 删除任务\n   111→     */\n   112→    public void delete(String id) {\n   113→        Task removed = tasksById.remove(id);\n   114→        if (removed != null) {\n   115→            taskList.remove(removed);\n   116→        }\n   117→    }\n   118→\n   119→    /**\n   120→     * 检查任务是否存在\n   121→     */\n   122→    public boolean exists(String id) {\n   123→        return tasksById.containsKey(id);\n   124→    }\n   125→\n   126→    /**\n   127→     * 获取任务数量\n   128→     */\n   129→    public int count() {\n   130→        return tasksById.size();\n   131→    }\n   132→\n   133→    /**\n   134→     * 清空所有任务\n   135→     */\n   136→    public void clear() {\n   137→        tasksById.clear();\n   138→        taskList.clear();\n   139→    }\n   140→}\n   141→\n   142→/**\n   143→ * CampusFlow Repository 测试类\n   144→ *\n   145→ * 测试覆盖目标：\n   146→ * - save: 正常保存、更新、异常输入\n   147→ * - findById: 存在、不存在\n   148→ * - findAll: 空集合、多个元素\n   149→ * - findByStatus: 按状态筛选\n   150→ * - delete: 删除存在/不存在的任务\n   151→ * - exists: 存在性检查\n   152→ */\n   153→class CampusFlowRepositoryTest {\n   154→\n   155→    private TaskRepository repository;\n   156→\n   157→    @BeforeEach\n   158→    void setUp() {\n   159→        repository = new TaskRepository();\n   160→    }\n   161→\n   162→    // ========== save 方法测试 ==========\n   163→\n   164→    @Test\n   165→    void shouldSaveTask() {\n   166→        Task task = new Task(\"T1\", \"完成 Week 06 作业\", \"pending\");\n   167→\n   168→        repository.save(task);\n   169→\n   170→        assertTrue(repository.findById(\"T1\").isPresent());\n   171→    }\n   172→\n   173→    @Test\n   174→    void shouldUpdateExistingTask() {\n   175→        Task task = new Task(\"T1\", \"完成任务\", \"pending\");\n   176→        repository.save(task);\n   177→\n   178→        // 更新任务\n   179→        Task updatedTask = new Task(\"T1\", \"完成任务（已修改）\", \"done\");\n   180→        repository.save(updatedTask);\n   181→\n   182→        Task found = repository.findById(\"T1\").orElseThrow();\n   183→        assertEquals(\"完成任务（已修改）\", found.getTitle());\n   184→        assertEquals(\"done\", found.getStatus());\n   185→    }\n   186→\n   187→    @Test\n   188→    void shouldThrowExceptionWhenSavingNull() {\n   189→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   190→            repository.save(null);\n   191→        });\n   192→    }\n   193→\n   194→    @Test\n   195→    void shouldThrowExceptionWhenSavingTaskWithNullId() {\n   196→        Task task = new Task(null, \"任务\", \"pending\");\n   197→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   198→            repository.save(task);\n   199→        });\n   200→    }\n   201→\n   202→    @Test\n   203→    void shouldThrowExceptionWhenSavingTaskWithEmptyId() {\n   204→        Task task = new Task(\"\", \"任务\", \"pending\");\n   205→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   206→            repository.save(task);\n   207→        });\n   208→    }\n   209→\n   210→    // ========== findById 方法测试 ==========\n   211→\n   212→    @Test\n   213→    void shouldFindTaskById() {\n   214→        repository.save(new Task(\"T1\", \"任务1\", \"pending\"));\n   215→\n   216→        java.util.Optional<Task> found = repository.findById(\"T1\");\n   217→\n   218→        assertTrue(found.isPresent());\n   219→        assertEquals(\"任务1\", found.get().getTitle());\n   220→    }\n   221→\n   222→    @Test\n   223→    void shouldReturnEmptyOptionalWhenTaskNotFound() {\n   224→        java.util.Optional<Task> found = repository.findById(\"不存在的ID\");\n   225→\n   226→        assertFalse(found.isPresent());\n   227→    }\n   228→\n   229→    // ========== findAll 方法测试 ==========\n   230→\n   231→    @Test\n   232→    void shouldFindAllTasks() {\n   233→        repository.save(new Task(\"T1\", \"任务1\", \"pending\"));\n   234→        repository.save(new Task(\"T2\", \"任务2\", \"done\"));\n   235→\n   236→        var tasks = repository.findAll();\n   237→\n   238→        assertEquals(2, tasks.size());\n   239→    }\n   240→\n   241→    @Test\n   242→    void shouldReturnEmptyListWhenNoTasks() {\n   243→        var tasks = repository.findAll();\n   244→\n   245→        assertTrue(tasks.isEmpty());\n   246→    }\n   247→\n   248→    @Test\n   249→    void findAllShouldReturnDefensiveCopy() {\n   250→        repository.save(new Task(\"T1\", \"任务1\", \"pending\"));\n   251→\n   252→        var tasks = repository.findAll();\n   253→        tasks.clear(); // 修改返回的列表\n   254→\n   255→        // 原始数据不应受影响\n   256→        assertEquals(1, repository.count());\n   257→    }\n   258→\n   259→    // ========== findByStatus 方法测试 ==========\n   260→\n   261→    @Test\n   262→    void shouldFindTasksByStatus() {\n   263→        repository.save(new Task(\"T1\", \"任务1\", \"pending\"));\n   264→        repository.save(new Task(\"T2\", \"任务2\", \"done\"));\n   265→        repository.save(new Task(\"T3\", \"任务3\", \"pending\"));\n   266→\n   267→        var pendingTasks = repository.findByStatus(\"pending\");\n   268→\n   269→        assertEquals(2, pendingTasks.size());\n   270→    }\n   271→\n   272→    @Test\n   273→    void shouldReturnEmptyListWhenNoTasksWithStatus() {\n   274→        repository.save(new Task(\"T1\", \"任务1\", \"done\"));\n   275→\n   276→        var pendingTasks = repository.findByStatus(\"pending\");\n   277→\n   278→        assertTrue(pendingTasks.isEmpty());\n   279→    }\n   280→\n   281→    // ========== delete 方法测试 ==========\n   282→\n   283→    @Test\n   284→    void shouldDeleteTask() {\n   285→        repository.save(new Task(\"T1\", \"任务\", \"pending\"));\n   286→        assertTrue(repository.findById(\"T1\").isPresent());\n   287→\n   288→        repository.delete(\"T1\");\n   289→\n   290→        assertFalse(repository.findById(\"T1\").isPresent());\n   291→    }\n   292→\n   293→    @Test\n   294→    void shouldNotThrowWhenDeletingNonExistentTask() {\n   295→        // 删除不存在的任务不应该抛出异常\n   296→        assertDoesNotThrow(() -> {\n   297→            repository.delete(\"不存在的ID\");\n   298→        });\n   299→    }\n   300→\n   301→    // ========== exists 方法测试 ==========\n   302→\n   303→    @Test\n   304→    void shouldReturnTrueWhenTaskExists() {\n   305→        repository.save(new Task(\"T1\", \"任务\", \"pending\"));\n   306→\n   307→        assertTrue(repository.exists(\"T1\"));\n   308→    }\n   309→\n   310→    @Test\n   311→    void shouldReturnFalseWhenTaskNotExists() {\n   312→        assertFalse(repository.exists(\"不存在的ID\"));\n   313→    }\n   314→\n   315→    // ========== count 方法测试 ==========\n   316→\n   317→    @Test\n   318→    void shouldReturnCorrectCount() {\n   319→        assertEquals(0, repository.count());\n   320→\n   321→        repository.save(new Task(\"T1\", \"任务1\", \"pending\"));\n   322→        assertEquals(1, repository.count());\n   323→\n   324→        repository.save(new Task(\"T2\", \"任务2\", \"done\"));\n   325→        assertEquals(2, repository.count());\n   326→    }\n   327→\n   328→    // ========== 参数化测试（批量验证） ==========\n   329→\n   330→    @ParameterizedTest\n   331→    @CsvSource({\n   332→        \"T1, 任务1, pending\",\n   333→        \"T2, 任务2, done\",\n   334→        \"T3, 任务3, in_progress\"\n   335→    })\n   336→    void shouldSaveAndRetrieveMultipleTasks(String id, String title, String status) {\n   337→        Task task = new Task(id, title, status);\n   338→        repository.save(task);\n   339→\n   340→        Task found = repository.findById(id).orElseThrow();\n   341→        assertEquals(title, found.getTitle());\n   342→        assertEquals(status, found.getStatus());\n   343→    }\n   344→\n   345→    // ========== 集成场景测试 ==========\n   346→\n   347→    @Test\n   348→    void shouldHandleCompleteTaskLifecycle() {\n   349→        // 创建 -> 查询 -> 更新 -> 查询 -> 删除\n   350→\n   351→        // 创建\n   352→        repository.save(new Task(\"T1\", \"完成任务\", \"pending\"));\n   353→        assertTrue(repository.exists(\"T1\"));\n   354→\n   355→        // 查询\n   356→        Task task = repository.findById(\"T1\").orElseThrow();\n   357→        assertEquals(\"pending\", task.getStatus());\n   358→\n   359→        // 更新（通过重新保存）\n   360→        repository.save(new Task(\"T1\", \"完成任务\", \"done\"));\n   361→        Task updated = repository.findById(\"T1\").orElseThrow();\n   362→        assertEquals(\"done\", updated.getStatus());\n   363→\n   364→        // 删除\n   365→        repository.delete(\"T1\");\n   366→        assertFalse(repository.exists(\"T1\"));\n   367→    }\n   368→\n   369→    @Test\n   370→    void shouldMaintainDataConsistencyBetweenFindByIdAndFindAll() {\n   371→        repository.save(new Task(\"T1\", \"任务1\", \"pending\"));\n   372→        repository.save(new Task(\"T2\", \"任务2\", \"done\"));\n   373→\n   374→        // findById 和 findAll 应该看到一致的数据\n   375→        assertEquals(2, repository.findAll().size());\n   376→        assertTrue(repository.findById(\"T1\").isPresent());\n   377→        assertTrue(repository.findById(\"T2\").isPresent());\n   378→\n   379→        // 删除后两者都应该看不到\n   380→        repository.delete(\"T1\");\n   381→        assertEquals(1, repository.findAll().size());\n   382→        assertFalse(repository.findById(\"T1\").isPresent());\n   383→    }\n   384→}\n   385→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_14f9c3afc6df478fbe525d70","session_id":"5071dd61-4cb8-490e-a97a-6edea443d84b","uuid":"dcefac36-df97-49ff-a94c-1a1f6fc896f4"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_4e646df5097f407081eb1c81","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→/*\n     2→ * 示例：参数化测试 - 使用 @ParameterizedTest 批量验证边界情况。\n     3→ * 运行方式：mvn -q -f chapters/week_06/starter_code/pom.xml test -Dtest=LibraryTrackerParameterizedTest\n     4→ * 预期输出：测试通过，每组参数生成一个独立的测试用例\n     5→ *\n     6→ * 关键概念：\n     7→ * - @ParameterizedTest: 标记参数化测试\n     8→ * - @ValueSource: 提供简单值列表\n     9→ * - @NullAndEmptySource: 专门提供 null 和空值\n    10→ * - @CsvSource: CSV 格式的表格数据\n    11→ * - @MethodSource: 引用方法提供参数（本例未展示）\n    12→ */\n    13→\n    14→import org.junit.jupiter.api.BeforeEach;\n    15→import org.junit.jupiter.params.ParameterizedTest;\n    16→import org.junit.jupiter.params.provider.CsvSource;\n    17→import org.junit.jupiter.params.provider.NullAndEmptySource;\n    18→import org.junit.jupiter.params.provider.ValueSource;\n    19→import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.*;\n    20→\n    21→/**\n    22→ * 图书类\n    23→ */\n    24→class Book {\n    25→    private String title;\n    26→    private String author;\n    27→    private String isbn;\n    28→\n    29→    public Book(String title, String author, String isbn) {\n    30→        this.title = title;\n    31→        this.author = author;\n    32→        this.isbn = isbn;\n    33→    }\n    34→\n    35→    public String getTitle() { return title; }\n    36→    public String getAuthor() { return author; }\n    37→    public String getIsbn() { return isbn; }\n    38→}\n    39→\n    40→/**\n    41→ * 借阅记录类\n    42→ */\n    43→class BorrowRecord {\n    44→    private String isbn;\n    45→    private String borrower;\n    46→\n    47→    public BorrowRecord(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    48→        this.isbn = isbn;\n    49→        this.borrower = borrower;\n    50→    }\n    51→\n    52→    public String getIsbn() { return isbn; }\n    53→    public String getBorrower() { return borrower; }\n    54→}\n    55→\n    56→/**\n    57→ * 图书追踪器\n    58→ */\n    59→class LibraryTracker {\n    60→    private java.util.HashMap<String, Book> booksByIsbn;\n    61→    private java.util.ArrayList<BorrowRecord> borrowRecords;\n    62→\n    63→    public LibraryTracker() {\n    64→        booksByIsbn = new java.util.HashMap<>();\n    65→        borrowRecords = new java.util.ArrayList<>();\n    66→    }\n    67→\n    68→    public void addBook(Book book) {\n    69→        if (book == null || book.getIsbn() == null) {\n    70→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书信息不完整\");\n    71→        }\n    72→        booksByIsbn.put(book.getIsbn(), book);\n    73→    }\n    74→\n    75→    public Book findBook(String isbn) {\n    76→        return booksByIsbn.get(isbn);\n    77→    }\n    78→\n    79→    public void borrowBook(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    80→        if (isbn == null || isbn.isEmpty()) {\n    81→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"ISBN 不能为空\");\n    82→        }\n    83→        if (borrower == null || borrower.isEmpty()) {\n    84→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"借阅人不能为空\");\n    85→        }\n    86→        if (!booksByIsbn.containsKey(isbn)) {\n    87→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书不存在：\" + isbn);\n    88→        }\n    89→        borrowRecords.add(new BorrowRecord(isbn, borrower));\n    90→    }\n    91→\n    92→    public boolean hasBorrowRecord(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    93→        for (BorrowRecord record : borrowRecords) {\n    94→            if (record.getIsbn().equals(isbn) && record.getBorrower().equals(borrower)) {\n    95→                return true;\n    96→            }\n    97→        }\n    98→        return false;\n    99→    }\n   100→}\n   101→\n   102→/**\n   103→ * 参数化测试类\n   104→ *\n   105→ * 反例（不使用参数化测试时的代码膨胀）：\n   106→ * ```java\n   107→ * @Test\n   108→ * void shouldRejectEmptyIsbn() { ... }\n   109→ *\n   110→ * @Test\n   111→ * void shouldRejectBlankIsbn() { ... }\n   112→ *\n   113→ * @Test\n   114→ * void shouldRejectNullIsbn() { ... }\n   115→ *\n   116→ * @Test\n   117→ * void shouldRejectInvalidIsbn() { ... }\n   118→ * // 重复的方法，几乎相同的代码\n   119→ * ```\n   120→ */\n   121→class LibraryTrackerParameterizedTest {\n   122→\n   123→    private LibraryTracker tracker;\n   124→\n   125→    @BeforeEach\n   126→    void setUp() {\n   127→        tracker = new LibraryTracker();\n   128→    }\n   129→\n   130→    /**\n   131→     * @ValueSource 用于提供简单的值列表（字符串、整数等）\n   132→     * 每个值会生成一个独立的测试用例\n   133→     */\n   134→    @ParameterizedTest\n   135→    @ValueSource(strings = {\"\", \"   \", \"invalid-isbn\", \"123\", \"ISBN@#$\"})\n   136→    void shouldRejectInvalidIsbn(String invalidIsbn) {\n   137→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书\", \"作者\", \"VALID-ISBN\"));\n   138→\n   139→        // 验证所有无效 ISBN 都应该抛出异常\n   140→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   141→            tracker.borrowBook(invalidIsbn, \"小北\");\n   142→        });\n   143→    }\n   144→\n   145→    /**\n   146→     * @NullAndEmptySource 专门用于测试 null 和空字符串\n   147→     * 这是边界测试的必备组合\n   148→     */\n   149→    @ParameterizedTest\n   150→    @NullAndEmptySource\n   151→    void shouldRejectNullOrEmptyIsbn(String invalidIsbn) {\n   152→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书\", \"作者\", \"VALID-ISBN\"));\n   153→\n   154→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   155→            tracker.borrowBook(invalidIsbn, \"小北\");\n   156→        });\n   157→    }\n   158→\n   159→    /**\n   160→     * @CsvSource 用于表格形式的数据\n   161→     * 格式：\"值1, 值2, 期望值\"\n   162→     * 适合测试输入-输出映射关系\n   163→     */\n   164→    @ParameterizedTest\n   165→    @CsvSource({\n   166→        \"ISBN-1, 小北, true\",    // 正常借阅\n   167→        \"ISBN-2, 小北, false\",   // 书不存在\n   168→        \"ISBN-1, 阿码, false\"    // 书存在但借给其他人了\n   169→    })\n   170→    void shouldCheckBorrowStatus(String isbn, String borrower, boolean expectedExists) {\n   171→        // 准备数据\n   172→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书1\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   173→        tracker.borrowBook(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\");\n   174→\n   175→        // 验证\n   176→        boolean exists = tracker.hasBorrowRecord(isbn, borrower);\n   177→        assertEquals(expectedExists, exists,\n   178→            String.format(\"查询 ISBN=%s, borrower=%s 应该返回 %b\", isbn, borrower, expectedExists));\n   179→    }\n   180→\n   181→    /**\n   182→     * 更复杂的 CSV 场景：多字段验证\n   183→     */\n   184→    @ParameterizedTest\n   185→    @CsvSource({\n   186→        \"T1, 任务1, pending\",\n   187→        \"T2, 任务2, done\",\n   188→        \"T3, 任务3, in_progress\"\n   189→    })\n   190→    void shouldAddAndRetrieveMultipleBooks(String isbn, String title, String author) {\n   191→        Book book = new Book(title, author, isbn);\n   192→        tracker.addBook(book);\n   193→\n   194→        Book found = tracker.findBook(isbn);\n   195→        assertNotNull(found);\n   196→        assertEquals(title, found.getTitle());\n   197→    }\n   198→\n   199→    /**\n   200→     * 可以组合多个数据源\n   201→     */\n   202→    @ParameterizedTest\n   203→    @ValueSource(strings = {\"\", \"   \"})\n   204→    @NullAndEmptySource\n   205→    void shouldRejectAllInvalidBorrowers(String invalidBorrower) {\n   206→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   207→\n   208→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   209→            tracker.borrowBook(\"ISBN-1\", invalidBorrower);\n   210→        });\n   211→    }\n   212→\n   213→    /**\n   214→     * 使用 name 属性自定义测试报告中的显示名称\n   215→     */\n   216→    @ParameterizedTest(name = \"[{index}] ISBN={0}, borrower={1} 应该返回 {2}\")\n   217→    @CsvSource({\n   218→        \"ISBN-1, 小北, true\",\n   219→        \"ISBN-2, 小北, false\"\n   220→    })\n   221→    void shouldCheckBorrowStatusWithCustomName(String isbn, String borrower, boolean expected) {\n   222→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书1\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   223→        tracker.borrowBook(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\");\n   224→\n   225→        assertEquals(expected, tracker.hasBorrowRecord(isbn, borrower));\n   226→    }\n   227→}\n   228→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_14f9c3afc6df478fbe525d70","session_id":"5071dd61-4cb8-490e-a97a-6edea443d84b","uuid":"9d87989e-65bc-4ea0-a4af-11eb3b9fc5e4"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_935f003f382c46ebb96d3e74","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→/*\n     2→ * 示例：第一个 JUnit 5 测试。\n     3→ * 运行方式：mvn -q -f chapters/week_06/starter_code/pom.xml test -Dtest=LibraryTrackerTest\n     4→ * 预期输出：测试通过，显示 \"Tests run: 2, Failures: 0\"\n     5→ *\n     6→ * Maven 依赖（pom.xml）:\n     7→ * <dependency>\n     8→ *     <groupId>org.junit.jupiter</groupId>\n     9→ *     <artifactId>junit-jupiter</artifactId>\n    10→ *     <version>5.11.0</version>\n    11→ *     <scope>test</scope>\n    12→ * </dependency>\n    13→ */\n    14→\n    15→import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n    16→import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.*;\n    17→\n    18→/**\n    19→ * 图书类 - 被测试的实体\n    20→ */\n    21→class Book {\n    22→    private String title;\n    23→    private String author;\n    24→    private String isbn;\n    25→\n    26→    public Book(String title, String author, String isbn) {\n    27→        this.title = title;\n    28→        this.author = author;\n    29→        this.isbn = isbn;\n    30→    }\n    31→\n    32→    public String getTitle() { return title; }\n    33→    public String getAuthor() { return author; }\n    34→    public String getIsbn() { return isbn; }\n    35→}\n    36→\n    37→/**\n    38→ * 正确的图书追踪器实现\n    39→ */\n    40→class LibraryTracker {\n    41→    private java.util.HashMap<String, Book> booksByIsbn;\n    42→    private java.util.ArrayList<BorrowRecord> borrowRecords;\n    43→\n    44→    public LibraryTracker() {\n    45→        booksByIsbn = new java.util.HashMap<>();\n    46→        borrowRecords = new java.util.ArrayList<>();\n    47→    }\n    48→\n    49→    public void addBook(Book book) {\n    50→        if (book == null || book.getIsbn() == null) {\n    51→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书信息不完整\");\n    52→        }\n    53→        booksByIsbn.put(book.getIsbn(), book);\n    54→    }\n    55→\n    56→    public Book findBook(String isbn) {\n    57→        return booksByIsbn.get(isbn);\n    58→    }\n    59→\n    60→    public void borrowBook(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    61→        if (isbn == null || isbn.isEmpty()) {\n    62→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"ISBN 不能为空\");\n    63→        }\n    64→        if (!booksByIsbn.containsKey(isbn)) {\n    65→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书不存在：\" + isbn);\n    66→        }\n    67→        borrowRecords.add(new BorrowRecord(isbn, borrower));\n    68→    }\n    69→\n    70→    public boolean hasBorrowRecord(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    71→        for (BorrowRecord record : borrowRecords) {\n    72→            if (record.getIsbn().equals(isbn) && record.getBorrower().equals(borrower)) {\n    73→                return true;\n    74→            }\n    75→        }\n    76→        return false;\n    77→    }\n    78→}\n    79→\n    80→/**\n    81→ * 借阅记录类\n    82→ */\n    83→class BorrowRecord {\n    84→    private String isbn;\n    85→    private String borrower;\n    86→\n    87→    public BorrowRecord(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    88→        this.isbn = isbn;\n    89→        this.borrower = borrower;\n    90→    }\n    91→\n    92→    public String getIsbn() { return isbn; }\n    93→    public String getBorrower() { return borrower; }\n    94→}\n    95→\n    96→/**\n    97→ * 第一个 JUnit 5 测试类\n    98→ *\n    99→ * 关键概念：\n   100→ * - @Test: 标记这是一个测试方法\n   101→ * - assertNotNull: 验证对象不为 null\n   102→ * - assertEquals: 验证两个值相等\n   103→ * - 测试方法命名规范：shouldXxxWhenYyy 或 should_xxx_when_yyy\n   104→ */\n   105→class LibraryTrackerTest {\n   106→\n   107→    @Test\n   108→    void shouldAddBookSuccessfully() {\n   109→        // 准备 (Arrange)\n   110→        LibraryTracker tracker = new LibraryTracker();\n   111→        Book book = new Book(\"Java 核心技术\", \"Cay Horstmann\", \"978-111\");\n   112→\n   113→        // 执行 (Act)\n   114→        tracker.addBook(book);\n   115→\n   116→        // 验证 (Assert)\n   117→        Book found = tracker.findBook(\"978-111\");\n   118→        assertNotNull(found, \"应该能找到添加的图书\");\n   119→        assertEquals(\"Java 核心技术\", found.getTitle(), \"书名应该匹配\");\n   120→        assertEquals(\"Cay Horstmann\", found.getAuthor(), \"作者应该匹配\");\n   121→    }\n   122→\n   123→    @Test\n   124→    void shouldFindBookByIsbn() {\n   125→        // 准备\n   126→        LibraryTracker tracker = new LibraryTracker();\n   127→        Book book1 = new Book(\"书1\", \"作者A\", \"ISBN-001\");\n   128→        Book book2 = new Book(\"书2\", \"作者B\", \"ISBN-002\");\n   129→\n   130→        // 执行\n   131→        tracker.addBook(book1);\n   132→        tracker.addBook(book2);\n   133→\n   134→        // 验证 - 用 HashMap 实现的查找应该是 O(1)\n   135→        Book found = tracker.findBook(\"ISBN-002\");\n   136→        assertNotNull(found);\n   137→        assertEquals(\"书2\", found.getTitle());\n   138→    }\n   139→}\n   140→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_14f9c3afc6df478fbe525d70","session_id":"5071dd61-4cb8-490e-a97a-6edea443d84b","uuid":"e8c50f32-39d5-489a-bb2d-ae42ca7048d2"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_1c85312ec63941408c4768b2","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→/*\n     2→ * 示例：完整测试覆盖 - 展示高覆盖率测试的写法。\n     3→ * 运行方式：mvn -q -f chapters/week_06/starter_code/pom.xml test -Dtest=LibraryTrackerCompleteTest\n     4→ * 预期输出：测试通过，覆盖率报告生成在 target/site/jacoco/index.html\n     5→ *\n     6→ * 关键概念：\n     7→ * - 行覆盖率：多少比例的代码行被执行\n     8→ * - 分支覆盖率：多少比例的 if/else 分支被执行\n     9→ * - 测试盲区：未被测试覆盖的代码区域\n    10→ *\n    11→ * JaCoCo Maven 插件配置（pom.xml）:\n    12→ * <plugin>\n    13→ *     <groupId>org.jacoco</groupId>\n    14→ *     <artifactId>jacoco-maven-plugin</artifactId>\n    15→ *     <version>0.8.12</version>\n    16→ *     <executions>\n    17→ *         <execution>\n    18→ *             <goals><goal>prepare-agent</goal></goals>\n    19→ *         </execution>\n    20→ *         <execution>\n    21→ *             <id>report</id>\n    22→ *             <phase>test</phase>\n    23→ *             <goals><goal>report</goal></goals>\n    24→ *         </execution>\n    25→ *     </executions>\n    26→ * </plugin>\n    27→ */\n    28→\n    29→import org.junit.jupiter.api.BeforeEach;\n    30→import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n    31→import org.junit.jupiter.params.ParameterizedTest;\n    32→import org.junit.jupiter.params.provider.CsvSource;\n    33→import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.*;\n    34→\n    35→/**\n    36→ * 图书类\n    37→ */\n    38→class Book {\n    39→    private String title;\n    40→    private String author;\n    41→    private String isbn;\n    42→\n    43→    public Book(String title, String author, String isbn) {\n    44→        this.title = title;\n    45→        this.author = author;\n    46→        this.isbn = isbn;\n    47→    }\n    48→\n    49→    public String getTitle() { return title; }\n    50→    public String getAuthor() { return author; }\n    51→    public String getIsbn() { return isbn; }\n    52→\n    53→    @Override\n    54→    public String toString() {\n    55→        return title + \" (\" + author + \")\";\n    56→    }\n    57→}\n    58→\n    59→/**\n    60→ * 借阅记录类\n    61→ */\n    62→class BorrowRecord {\n    63→    private String isbn;\n    64→    private String borrower;\n    65→    private java.time.LocalDate borrowDate;\n    66→\n    67→    public BorrowRecord(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    68→        this.isbn = isbn;\n    69→        this.borrower = borrower;\n    70→        this.borrowDate = java.time.LocalDate.now();\n    71→    }\n    72→\n    73→    public String getIsbn() { return isbn; }\n    74→    public String getBorrower() { return borrower; }\n    75→    public java.time.LocalDate getBorrowDate() { return borrowDate; }\n    76→}\n    77→\n    78→/**\n    79→ * 完整的图书追踪器实现\n    80→ * 目标：通过完整测试达到 80%+ 覆盖率\n    81→ */\n    82→class LibraryTracker {\n    83→    private java.util.HashMap<String, Book> booksByIsbn;\n    84→    private java.util.ArrayList<BorrowRecord> borrowRecords;\n    85→\n    86→    public LibraryTracker() {\n    87→        booksByIsbn = new java.util.HashMap<>();\n    88→        borrowRecords = new java.util.ArrayList<>();\n    89→    }\n    90→\n    91→    // ========== 图书管理 ==========\n    92→\n    93→    public void addBook(Book book) {\n    94→        if (book == null) {\n    95→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书不能为空\");\n    96→        }\n    97→        if (book.getIsbn() == null || book.getIsbn().isEmpty()) {\n    98→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"ISBN 不能为空\");\n    99→        }\n   100→        booksByIsbn.put(book.getIsbn(), book);\n   101→    }\n   102→\n   103→    public Book findBook(String isbn) {\n   104→        return booksByIsbn.get(isbn);\n   105→    }\n   106→\n   107→    public java.util.List<Book> listAllBooks() {\n   108→        return new java.util.ArrayList<>(booksByIsbn.values());\n   109→    }\n   110→\n   111→    public void removeBook(String isbn) {\n   112→        booksByIsbn.remove(isbn);\n   113→        // 同时清理相关借阅记录\n   114→        borrowRecords.removeIf(r -> r.getIsbn().equals(isbn));\n   115→    }\n   116→\n   117→    public int getBookCount() {\n   118→        return booksByIsbn.size();\n   119→    }\n   120→\n   121→    // ========== 借阅管理 ==========\n   122→\n   123→    public void borrowBook(String isbn, String borrower) {\n   124→        if (isbn == null || isbn.isEmpty()) {\n   125→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"ISBN 不能为空\");\n   126→        }\n   127→        if (borrower == null || borrower.isEmpty()) {\n   128→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"借阅人不能为空\");\n   129→        }\n   130→        if (!booksByIsbn.containsKey(isbn)) {\n   131→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书不存在：\" + isbn);\n   132→        }\n   133→        borrowRecords.add(new BorrowRecord(isbn, borrower));\n   134→    }\n   135→\n   136→    public void returnBook(String isbn, String borrower) {\n   137→        java.util.Iterator<BorrowRecord> it = borrowRecords.iterator();\n   138→        while (it.hasNext()) {\n   139→            BorrowRecord record = it.next();\n   140→            if (record.getIsbn().equals(isbn) && record.getBorrower().equals(borrower)) {\n   141→                it.remove();\n   142→                return;\n   143→            }\n   144→        }\n   145→        throw new IllegalStateException(\"未找到对应的借阅记录\");\n   146→    }\n   147→\n   148→    public boolean hasBorrowRecord(String isbn, String borrower) {\n   149→        for (BorrowRecord record : borrowRecords) {\n   150→            if (record.getIsbn().equals(isbn) && record.getBorrower().equals(borrower)) {\n   151→                return true;\n   152→            }\n   153→        }\n   154→        return false;\n   155→    }\n   156→\n   157→    public java.util.List<BorrowRecord> getAllBorrowRecords() {\n   158→        return new java.util.ArrayList<>(borrowRecords);\n   159→    }\n   160→\n   161→    public int getBorrowRecordCount() {\n   162→        return borrowRecords.size();\n   163→    }\n   164→}\n   165→\n   166→/**\n   167→ * 完整测试类 - 目标覆盖率 80%+\n   168→ *\n   169→ * 测试策略：\n   170→ * 1. 正常路径测试：验证功能正确性\n   171→ * 2. 异常路径测试：验证防御式编程\n   172→ * 3. 边界情况测试：空值、空集合等\n   173→ * 4. 集成场景测试：多操作组合\n   174→ */\n   175→class LibraryTrackerCompleteTest {\n   176→\n   177→    private LibraryTracker tracker;\n   178→\n   179→    @BeforeEach\n   180→    void setUp() {\n   181→        tracker = new LibraryTracker();\n   182→    }\n   183→\n   184→    // ========== 图书管理测试 ==========\n   185→\n   186→    @Test\n   187→    void shouldAddBookSuccessfully() {\n   188→        Book book = new Book(\"Java 核心技术\", \"Cay Horstmann\", \"978-111\");\n   189→\n   190→        tracker.addBook(book);\n   191→\n   192→        Book found = tracker.findBook(\"978-111\");\n   193→        assertNotNull(found);\n   194→        assertEquals(\"Java 核心技术\", found.getTitle());\n   195→    }\n   196→\n   197→    @Test\n   198→    void shouldListAllBooks() {\n   199→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书1\", \"作者A\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   200→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书2\", \"作者B\", \"ISBN-2\"));\n   201→\n   202→        var books = tracker.listAllBooks();\n   203→\n   204→        assertEquals(2, books.size());\n   205→    }\n   206→\n   207→    @Test\n   208→    void shouldRemoveBook() {\n   209→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   210→        assertNotNull(tracker.findBook(\"ISBN-1\"));\n   211→\n   212→        tracker.removeBook(\"ISBN-1\");\n   213→\n   214→        assertNull(tracker.findBook(\"ISBN-1\"));\n   215→    }\n   216→\n   217→    @Test\n   218→    void shouldRemoveBookAndRelatedBorrowRecords() {\n   219→        // 添加书并借阅\n   220→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   221→        tracker.borrowBook(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\");\n   222→        assertTrue(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\"));\n   223→\n   224→        // 删除书时应该同时清理借阅记录\n   225→        tracker.removeBook(\"ISBN-1\");\n   226→\n   227→        assertEquals(0, tracker.getBorrowRecordCount());\n   228→    }\n   229→\n   230→    @Test\n   231→    void shouldReturnEmptyListWhenNoBooks() {\n   232→        var books = tracker.listAllBooks();\n   233→        assertTrue(books.isEmpty());\n   234→    }\n   235→\n   236→    @Test\n   237→    void shouldReturnNullForNonExistentBook() {\n   238→        Book found = tracker.findBook(\"不存在的ISBN\");\n   239→        assertNull(found);\n   240→    }\n   241→\n   242→    @Test\n   243→    void shouldGetBookCount() {\n   244→        assertEquals(0, tracker.getBookCount());\n   245→\n   246→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书1\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   247→        assertEquals(1, tracker.getBookCount());\n   248→\n   249→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书2\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-2\"));\n   250→        assertEquals(2, tracker.getBookCount());\n   251→    }\n   252→\n   253→    // ========== 借阅管理测试 ==========\n   254→\n   255→    @Test\n   256→    void shouldBorrowBookSuccessfully() {\n   257→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   258→\n   259→        tracker.borrowBook(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\");\n   260→\n   261→        assertTrue(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\"));\n   262→    }\n   263→\n   264→    @Test\n   265→    void shouldReturnBookSuccessfully() {\n   266→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   267→        tracker.borrowBook(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\");\n   268→        assertTrue(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\"));\n   269→\n   270→        tracker.returnBook(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\");\n   271→\n   272→        assertFalse(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\"));\n   273→    }\n   274→\n   275→    @Test\n   276→    void shouldGetAllBorrowRecords() {\n   277→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书1\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   278→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书2\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-2\"));\n   279→        tracker.borrowBook(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\");\n   280→        tracker.borrowBook(\"ISBN-2\", \"阿码\");\n   281→\n   282→        var records = tracker.getAllBorrowRecords();\n   283→\n   284→        assertEquals(2, records.size());\n   285→    }\n   286→\n   287→    @Test\n   288→    void shouldGetBorrowRecordCount() {\n   289→        assertEquals(0, tracker.getBorrowRecordCount());\n   290→\n   291→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   292→        tracker.borrowBook(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\");\n   293→\n   294→        assertEquals(1, tracker.getBorrowRecordCount());\n   295→    }\n   296→\n   297→    // ========== 异常测试 ==========\n   298→\n   299→    @Test\n   300→    void shouldThrowExceptionWhenAddingNullBook() {\n   301→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   302→            tracker.addBook(null);\n   303→        });\n   304→    }\n   305→\n   306→    @Test\n   307→    void shouldThrowExceptionWhenAddingBookWithNullIsbn() {\n   308→        Book book = new Book(\"书\", \"作者\", null);\n   309→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   310→            tracker.addBook(book);\n   311→        });\n   312→    }\n   313→\n   314→    @Test\n   315→    void shouldThrowExceptionWhenBorrowingNonExistentBook() {\n   316→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   317→            tracker.borrowBook(\"不存在的ISBN\", \"小北\");\n   318→        });\n   319→    }\n   320→\n   321→    @Test\n   322→    void shouldThrowExceptionWhenReturningNonExistentRecord() {\n   323→        assertThrows(IllegalStateException.class, () -> {\n   324→            tracker.returnBook(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\");\n   325→        });\n   326→    }\n   327→\n   328→    // ========== 参数化测试（批量边界验证） ==========\n   329→\n   330→    @ParameterizedTest\n   331→    @CsvSource({\n   332→        \"ISBN-1, 小北, true\",\n   333→        \"ISBN-2, 小北, false\",\n   334→        \"ISBN-1, 阿码, false\"\n   335→    })\n   336→    void shouldCheckBorrowStatus(String isbn, String borrower, boolean expected) {\n   337→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书1\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   338→        tracker.borrowBook(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\");\n   339→\n   340→        assertEquals(expected, tracker.hasBorrowRecord(isbn, borrower));\n   341→    }\n   342→\n   343→    // ========== 集成场景测试 ==========\n   344→\n   345→    @Test\n   346→    void shouldHandleCompleteBorrowingWorkflow() {\n   347→        // 完整借阅流程：添加 -> 借阅 -> 验证 -> 归还 -> 验证\n   348→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"Java 核心技术\", \"Cay\", \"978-111\"));\n   349→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"Effective Java\", \"Joshua\", \"978-222\"));\n   350→\n   351→        // 借阅\n   352→        tracker.borrowBook(\"978-111\", \"小北\");\n   353→        tracker.borrowBook(\"978-222\", \"阿码\");\n   354→\n   355→        assertEquals(2, tracker.getBorrowRecordCount());\n   356→        assertTrue(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"978-111\", \"小北\"));\n   357→        assertTrue(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"978-222\", \"阿码\"));\n   358→\n   359→        // 归还\n   360→        tracker.returnBook(\"978-111\", \"小北\");\n   361→\n   362→        assertEquals(1, tracker.getBorrowRecordCount());\n   363→        assertFalse(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"978-111\", \"小北\"));\n   364→        assertTrue(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"978-222\", \"阿码\"));\n   365→    }\n   366→\n   367→    @Test\n   368→    void shouldAllowMultipleBorrowsBySamePerson() {\n   369→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书1\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   370→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书2\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-2\"));\n   371→\n   372→        tracker.borrowBook(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\");\n   373→        tracker.borrowBook(\"ISBN-2\", \"小北\");\n   374→\n   375→        assertEquals(2, tracker.getBorrowRecordCount());\n   376→        assertTrue(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\"));\n   377→        assertTrue(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"ISBN-2\", \"小北\"));\n   378→    }\n   379→}\n   380→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_14f9c3afc6df478fbe525d70","session_id":"5071dd61-4cb8-490e-a97a-6edea443d84b","uuid":"2aa0b3ea-e58d-44a1-b08e-b8ab0ab40612"}
