{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_40ef14610ea94ea2b566f9ac","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package com.campusflow;\n     2→\n     3→import java.util.Objects;\n     4→\n     5→/**\n     6→ * 图书实体类\n     7→ * 表示图书馆中的一本书，包含基本信息和借阅状态\n     8→ */\n     9→public class Book {\n    10→    private final String title;\n    11→    private final String author;\n    12→    private final String isbn;\n    13→    private boolean borrowed;\n    14→    private String borrower;\n    15→\n    16→    /**\n    17→     * 创建一本新书\n    18→     *\n    19→     * @param title  书名\n    20→     * @param author 作者\n    21→     * @param isbn   ISBN编号\n    22→     * @throws IllegalArgumentException 如果 title、author 或 isbn 为空\n    23→     */\n    24→    public Book(String title, String author, String isbn) {\n    25→        if (title == null || title.trim().isEmpty()) {\n    26→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"书名不能为空\");\n    27→        }\n    28→        if (author == null || author.trim().isEmpty()) {\n    29→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"作者不能为空\");\n    30→        }\n    31→        if (isbn == null || isbn.trim().isEmpty()) {\n    32→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"ISBN 不能为空\");\n    33→        }\n    34→        this.title = title;\n    35→        this.author = author;\n    36→        this.isbn = isbn;\n    37→        this.borrowed = false;\n    38→        this.borrower = null;\n    39→    }\n    40→\n    41→    public String getTitle() {\n    42→        return title;\n    43→    }\n    44→\n    45→    public String getAuthor() {\n    46→        return author;\n    47→    }\n    48→\n    49→    public String getIsbn() {\n    50→        return isbn;\n    51→    }\n    52→\n    53→    public boolean isBorrowed() {\n    54→        return borrowed;\n    55→    }\n    56→\n    57→    public String getBorrower() {\n    58→        return borrower;\n    59→    }\n    60→\n    61→    /**\n    62→     * 标记图书为已借出\n    63→     *\n    64→     * @param borrowerName 借阅人姓名\n    65→     * @throws IllegalArgumentException 如果 borrowerName 为空\n    66→     */\n    67→    public void markAsBorrowed(String borrowerName) {\n    68→        if (borrowerName == null || borrowerName.trim().isEmpty()) {\n    69→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"借阅人不能为空\");\n    70→        }\n    71→        this.borrowed = true;\n    72→        this.borrower = borrowerName;\n    73→    }\n    74→\n    75→    /**\n    76→     * 标记图书为已归还\n    77→     */\n    78→    public void markAsReturned() {\n    79→        this.borrowed = false;\n    80→        this.borrower = null;\n    81→    }\n    82→\n    83→    @Override\n    84→    public boolean equals(Object o) {\n    85→        if (this == o) return true;\n    86→        if (o == null || getClass() != o.getClass()) return false;\n    87→        Book book = (Book) o;\n    88→        return Objects.equals(isbn, book.isbn);\n    89→    }\n    90→\n    91→    @Override\n    92→    public int hashCode() {\n    93→        return Objects.hash(isbn);\n    94→    }\n    95→\n    96→    @Override\n    97→    public String toString() {\n    98→        return \"Book{\" +\n    99→                \"title='\" + title + '\\'' +\n   100→                \", author='\" + author + '\\'' +\n   101→                \", isbn='\" + isbn + '\\'' +\n   102→                \", borrowed=\" + borrowed +\n   103→                \", borrower='\" + borrower + '\\'' +\n   104→                '}';\n   105→    }\n   106→}\n   107→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_14f9c3afc6df478fbe525d70","session_id":"5071dd61-4cb8-490e-a97a-6edea443d84b","uuid":"fde4f399-a548-4d21-95d9-b15a319b7144"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_bbd8991e8d334ccdbec9ba9a","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package com.campusflow;\n     2→\n     3→import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n     4→import org.junit.jupiter.params.ParameterizedTest;\n     5→import org.junit.jupiter.params.provider.CsvSource;\n     6→import org.junit.jupiter.params.provider.NullAndEmptySource;\n     7→import org.junit.jupiter.params.provider.ValueSource;\n     8→\n     9→import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.*;\n    10→\n    11→/**\n    12→ * Book 实体类测试\n    13→ * 覆盖构造器验证、借阅状态转换、equals/hashCode 等\n    14→ */\n    15→public class BookTest {\n    16→\n    17→    // ==================== 构造器测试 ====================\n    18→\n    19→    @Test\n    20→    void constructor_WithValidInput_ShouldCreateBook() {\n    21→        Book book = new Book(\"Java 核心技术\", \"Cay Horstmann\", \"978-111\");\n    22→\n    23→        assertAll(\"图书属性应正确设置\",\n    24→            () -> assertEquals(\"Java 核心技术\", book.getTitle()),\n    25→            () -> assertEquals(\"Cay Horstmann\", book.getAuthor()),\n    26→            () -> assertEquals(\"978-111\", book.getIsbn()),\n    27→            () -> assertFalse(book.isBorrowed()),\n    28→            () -> assertNull(book.getBorrower())\n    29→        );\n    30→    }\n    31→\n    32→    @ParameterizedTest\n    33→    @NullAndEmptySource\n    34→    @ValueSource(strings = {\"   \", \"\\t\", \"\\n\"})\n    35→    void constructor_WithInvalidTitle_ShouldThrowException(String invalidTitle) {\n    36→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n    37→            new Book(invalidTitle, \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\");\n    38→        });\n    39→    }\n    40→\n    41→    @ParameterizedTest\n    42→    @NullAndEmptySource\n    43→    @ValueSource(strings = {\"   \", \"\\t\"})\n    44→    void constructor_WithInvalidAuthor_ShouldThrowException(String invalidAuthor) {\n    45→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n    46→            new Book(\"书名\", invalidAuthor, \"ISBN-1\");\n    47→        });\n    48→    }\n    49→\n    50→    @ParameterizedTest\n    51→    @NullAndEmptySource\n    52→    @ValueSource(strings = {\"   \", \"\\t\"})\n    53→    void constructor_WithInvalidIsbn_ShouldThrowException(String invalidIsbn) {\n    54→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n    55→            new Book(\"书名\", \"作者\", invalidIsbn);\n    56→        });\n    57→    }\n    58→\n    59→    // ==================== 借阅状态测试 ====================\n    60→\n    61→    @Test\n    62→    void markAsBorrowed_WithValidBorrower_ShouldSetBorrowedState() {\n    63→        Book book = new Book(\"测试书\", \"测试作者\", \"ISBN-1\");\n    64→\n    65→        book.markAsBorrowed(\"小北\");\n    66→\n    67→        assertAll(\"借阅后状态\",\n    68→            () -> assertTrue(book.isBorrowed()),\n    69→            () -> assertEquals(\"小北\", book.getBorrower())\n    70→        );\n    71→    }\n    72→\n    73→    @ParameterizedTest\n    74→    @NullAndEmptySource\n    75→    @ValueSource(strings = {\"   \", \"\\t\"})\n    76→    void markAsBorrowed_WithInvalidBorrower_ShouldThrowException(String invalidBorrower) {\n    77→        Book book = new Book(\"测试书\", \"测试作者\", \"ISBN-1\");\n    78→\n    79→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n    80→            book.markAsBorrowed(invalidBorrower);\n    81→        });\n    82→    }\n    83→\n    84→    @Test\n    85→    void markAsReturned_ShouldClearBorrowedState() {\n    86→        Book book = new Book(\"测试书\", \"测试作者\", \"ISBN-1\");\n    87→        book.markAsBorrowed(\"小北\");\n    88→        assertTrue(book.isBorrowed());\n    89→\n    90→        book.markAsReturned();\n    91→\n    92→        assertAll(\"归还后状态\",\n    93→            () -> assertFalse(book.isBorrowed()),\n    94→            () -> assertNull(book.getBorrower())\n    95→        );\n    96→    }\n    97→\n    98→    // ==================== equals/hashCode 测试 ====================\n    99→\n   100→    @Test\n   101→    void equals_WithSameIsbn_ShouldReturnTrue() {\n   102→        Book book1 = new Book(\"书1\", \"作者A\", \"ISBN-001\");\n   103→        Book book2 = new Book(\"书2\", \"作者B\", \"ISBN-001\");\n   104→\n   105→        assertEquals(book1, book2, \"相同 ISBN 的图书应相等\");\n   106→    }\n   107→\n   108→    @Test\n   109→    void equals_WithDifferentIsbn_ShouldReturnFalse() {\n   110→        Book book1 = new Book(\"书1\", \"作者A\", \"ISBN-001\");\n   111→        Book book2 = new Book(\"书1\", \"作者A\", \"ISBN-002\");\n   112→\n   113→        assertNotEquals(book1, book2, \"不同 ISBN 的图书不应相等\");\n   114→    }\n   115→\n   116→    @Test\n   117→    void equals_WithSameObject_ShouldReturnTrue() {\n   118→        Book book = new Book(\"书1\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-001\");\n   119→\n   120→        assertEquals(book, book, \"同一对象应相等\");\n   121→    }\n   122→\n   123→    @Test\n   124→    void equals_WithNull_ShouldReturnFalse() {\n   125→        Book book = new Book(\"书1\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-001\");\n   126→\n   127→        assertNotEquals(null, book, \"与 null 比较应返回 false\");\n   128→    }\n   129→\n   130→    @Test\n   131→    void equals_WithDifferentClass_ShouldReturnFalse() {\n   132→        Book book = new Book(\"书1\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-001\");\n   133→\n   134→        assertNotEquals(book, \"ISBN-001\", \"与不同类对象比较应返回 false\");\n   135→    }\n   136→\n   137→    @Test\n   138→    void hashCode_WithSameIsbn_ShouldBeEqual() {\n   139→        Book book1 = new Book(\"书1\", \"作者A\", \"ISBN-001\");\n   140→        Book book2 = new Book(\"书2\", \"作者B\", \"ISBN-001\");\n   141→\n   142→        assertEquals(book1.hashCode(), book2.hashCode(), \"相同 ISBN 的图书 hashCode 应相等\");\n   143→    }\n   144→\n   145→    // ==================== toString 测试 ====================\n   146→\n   147→    @Test\n   148→    void toString_ShouldContainBookInfo() {\n   149→        Book book = new Book(\"Java编程\", \"张三\", \"ISBN-123\");\n   150→\n   151→        String str = book.toString();\n   152→\n   153→        assertAll(\"toString 应包含图书信息\",\n   154→            () -> assertTrue(str.contains(\"Java编程\")),\n   155→            () -> assertTrue(str.contains(\"张三\")),\n   156→            () -> assertTrue(str.contains(\"ISBN-123\"))\n   157→        );\n   158→    }\n   159→\n   160→    @Test\n   161→    void toString_WithBorrowedBook_ShouldContainBorrowerInfo() {\n   162→        Book book = new Book(\"Java编程\", \"张三\", \"ISBN-123\");\n   163→        book.markAsBorrowed(\"小北\");\n   164→\n   165→        String str = book.toString();\n   166→\n   167→        assertTrue(str.contains(\"小北\"), \"toString 应包含借阅人信息\");\n   168→    }\n   169→\n   170→    // ==================== 完整生命周期测试 ====================\n   171→\n   172→    @ParameterizedTest(name = \"借阅人={0}\")\n   173→    @CsvSource({\n   174→        \"小北\",\n   175→        \"阿码\",\n   176→        \"老潘\"\n   177→    })\n   178→    void bookFullLifecycle_ShouldWorkCorrectly(String borrower) {\n   179→        // 创建\n   180→        Book book = new Book(\"测试书\", \"测试作者\", \"ISBN-LIFE\");\n   181→        assertFalse(book.isBorrowed());\n   182→\n   183→        // 借阅\n   184→        book.markAsBorrowed(borrower);\n   185→        assertTrue(book.isBorrowed());\n   186→        assertEquals(borrower, book.getBorrower());\n   187→\n   188→        // 归还\n   189→        book.markAsReturned();\n   190→        assertFalse(book.isBorrowed());\n   191→        assertNull(book.getBorrower());\n   192→    }\n   193→}\n   194→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_14f9c3afc6df478fbe525d70","session_id":"5071dd61-4cb8-490e-a97a-6edea443d84b","uuid":"8ee6a730-1ddd-445b-9317-122ed0a49edb"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_35f5dc95774c442fb2de9e66","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package com.campusflow;\n     2→\n     3→import java.util.*;\n     4→\n     5→/**\n     6→ * 图书借阅追踪器\n     7→ * 管理图书的添加、查询、借阅和归还操作\n     8→ */\n     9→public class LibraryTracker {\n    10→\n    11→    private final Map<String, Book> booksByIsbn;\n    12→\n    13→    public LibraryTracker() {\n    14→        this.booksByIsbn = new HashMap<>();\n    15→    }\n    16→\n    17→    /**\n    18→     * 添加图书到追踪器\n    19→     *\n    20→     * @param book 要添加的图书\n    21→     * @throws IllegalArgumentException 如果 book 为 null 或 ISBN 为空\n    22→     */\n    23→    public void addBook(Book book) {\n    24→        if (book == null) {\n    25→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书不能为空\");\n    26→        }\n    27→        if (book.getIsbn() == null || book.getIsbn().trim().isEmpty()) {\n    28→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"ISBN 不能为空\");\n    29→        }\n    30→        // 如果 ISBN 已存在，更新图书信息（覆盖）\n    31→        booksByIsbn.put(book.getIsbn(), book);\n    32→    }\n    33→\n    34→    /**\n    35→     * 根据 ISBN 查找图书\n    36→     *\n    37→     * @param isbn ISBN 编号\n    38→     * @return 找到的图书，如果不存在返回 null\n    39→     * @throws IllegalArgumentException 如果 isbn 为 null\n    40→     */\n    41→    public Book findByIsbn(String isbn) {\n    42→        if (isbn == null) {\n    43→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"ISBN 不能为 null\");\n    44→        }\n    45→        return booksByIsbn.get(isbn);\n    46→    }\n    47→\n    48→    /**\n    49→     * 借阅图书\n    50→     *\n    51→     * @param isbn     图书 ISBN\n    52→     * @param borrower 借阅人姓名\n    53→     * @throws IllegalArgumentException 如果图书不存在、已被借出或借阅人为空\n    54→     */\n    55→    public void borrowBook(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    56→        if (isbn == null || isbn.trim().isEmpty()) {\n    57→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"ISBN 不能为空\");\n    58→        }\n    59→        if (borrower == null || borrower.trim().isEmpty()) {\n    60→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"借阅人不能为空\");\n    61→        }\n    62→\n    63→        Book book = booksByIsbn.get(isbn);\n    64→        if (book == null) {\n    65→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书不存在: \" + isbn);\n    66→        }\n    67→        if (book.isBorrowed()) {\n    68→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书已被借出: \" + isbn);\n    69→        }\n    70→\n    71→        book.markAsBorrowed(borrower);\n    72→    }\n    73→\n    74→    /**\n    75→     * 归还图书\n    76→     *\n    77→     * @param isbn     图书 ISBN\n    78→     * @param borrower 借阅人姓名\n    79→     * @throws IllegalArgumentException 如果图书不存在、未被借出或借阅人不匹配\n    80→     */\n    81→    public void returnBook(String isbn, String borrower) {\n    82→        if (isbn == null || isbn.trim().isEmpty()) {\n    83→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"ISBN 不能为空\");\n    84→        }\n    85→        if (borrower == null || borrower.trim().isEmpty()) {\n    86→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"借阅人不能为空\");\n    87→        }\n    88→\n    89→        Book book = booksByIsbn.get(isbn);\n    90→        if (book == null) {\n    91→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书不存在: \" + isbn);\n    92→        }\n    93→        if (!book.isBorrowed()) {\n    94→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"图书未被借出: \" + isbn);\n    95→        }\n    96→        if (!borrower.equals(book.getBorrower())) {\n    97→            throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"归还人与借阅人不符，借阅人是: \" + book.getBorrower());\n    98→        }\n    99→\n   100→        book.markAsReturned();\n   101→    }\n   102→\n   103→    /**\n   104→     * 检查是否存在指定的借阅记录\n   105→     *\n   106→     * @param isbn     图书 ISBN\n   107→     * @param borrower 借阅人姓名\n   108→     * @return 如果存在该借阅记录返回 true\n   109→     */\n   110→    public boolean hasBorrowRecord(String isbn, String borrower) {\n   111→        if (isbn == null || borrower == null) {\n   112→            return false;\n   113→        }\n   114→        Book book = booksByIsbn.get(isbn);\n   115→        if (book == null) {\n   116→            return false;\n   117→        }\n   118→        return book.isBorrowed() && borrower.equals(book.getBorrower());\n   119→    }\n   120→\n   121→    /**\n   122→     * 列出所有图书\n   123→     *\n   124→     * @return 所有图书的列表\n   125→     */\n   126→    public List<Book> listAllBooks() {\n   127→        return new ArrayList<>(booksByIsbn.values());\n   128→    }\n   129→\n   130→    /**\n   131→     * 移除图书\n   132→     *\n   133→     * @param isbn 图书 ISBN\n   134→     * @return 如果成功移除返回 true，如果图书不存在返回 false\n   135→     */\n   136→    public boolean removeBook(String isbn) {\n   137→        if (isbn == null || isbn.trim().isEmpty()) {\n   138→            return false;\n   139→        }\n   140→        return booksByIsbn.remove(isbn) != null;\n   141→    }\n   142→\n   143→    /**\n   144→     * 获取图书总数\n   145→     *\n   146→     * @return 图书总数\n   147→     */\n   148→    public int getBookCount() {\n   149→        return booksByIsbn.size();\n   150→    }\n   151→}\n   152→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_14f9c3afc6df478fbe525d70","session_id":"5071dd61-4cb8-490e-a97a-6edea443d84b","uuid":"85d7c0d6-1f20-45a3-b7e0-4f8ff031bdac"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_3a4333bd50b3456ea3ad0856","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package com.campusflow;\n     2→\n     3→import org.junit.jupiter.api.BeforeEach;\n     4→import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n     5→import org.junit.jupiter.params.ParameterizedTest;\n     6→import org.junit.jupiter.params.provider.CsvSource;\n     7→import org.junit.jupiter.params.provider.NullAndEmptySource;\n     8→import org.junit.jupiter.params.provider.ValueSource;\n     9→\n    10→import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.*;\n    11→\n    12→/**\n    13→ * LibraryTracker 完整测试类\n    14→ * 覆盖 addBook, findByIsbn, borrowBook, returnBook 等核心方法\n    15→ *\n    16→ * 测试用例矩阵：\n    17→ * - addBook: 正例(正常添加)、边界(null/空ISBN)、反例(重复添加覆盖)\n    18→ * - findByIsbn: 正例(找到图书)、边界(不存在返回null)、边界(传入null抛异常)\n    19→ * - borrowBook: 正例(正常借书)、边界(书不存在抛异常)、边界(借阅人为空抛异常)\n    20→ * - returnBook: 正例(正常还书)、边界(未借出抛异常)、边界(错误借阅人抛异常)\n    21→ */\n    22→public class LibraryTrackerTest {\n    23→\n    24→    private LibraryTracker tracker;\n    25→    private Book testBook;\n    26→\n    27→    @BeforeEach\n    28→    void setUp() {\n    29→        tracker = new LibraryTracker();\n    30→        testBook = new Book(\"Java 核心技术\", \"Cay Horstmann\", \"978-111\");\n    31→    }\n    32→\n    33→    // ==================== addBook 测试 ====================\n    34→\n    35→    /**\n    36→     * 测试类型：正例\n    37→     * 输入数据：正常图书对象\n    38→     * 预期结果：图书成功添加，可通过 ISBN 找到\n    39→     * JUnit 特性：基本断言 assertNotNull, assertEquals\n    40→     */\n    41→    @Test\n    42→    void addBook_WithValidBook_ShouldAddSuccessfully() {\n    43→        // 执行\n    44→        tracker.addBook(testBook);\n    45→\n    46→        // 验证\n    47→        Book found = tracker.findByIsbn(\"978-111\");\n    48→        assertNotNull(found, \"添加的图书应该能被找到\");\n    49→        assertEquals(\"Java 核心技术\", found.getTitle());\n    50→        assertEquals(\"Cay Horstmann\", found.getAuthor());\n    51→    }\n    52→\n    53→    /**\n    54→     * 测试类型：边界 - null 输入\n    55→     * 输入数据：null\n    56→     * 预期结果：抛出 IllegalArgumentException\n    57→     * JUnit 特性：assertThrows\n    58→     */\n    59→    @Test\n    60→    void addBook_WithNullBook_ShouldThrowException() {\n    61→        Exception exception = assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n    62→            tracker.addBook(null);\n    63→        });\n    64→        assertEquals(\"图书不能为空\", exception.getMessage());\n    65→    }\n    66→\n    67→    /**\n    68→     * 测试类型：边界 - 空 ISBN\n    69→     * 输入数据：ISBN 为空的图书\n    70→     * 预期结果：抛出 IllegalArgumentException（在 Book 构造时）\n    71→     * JUnit 特性：assertThrows\n    72→     */\n    73→    @Test\n    74→    void addBook_WithEmptyIsbn_ShouldThrowException() {\n    75→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n    76→            Book bookWithEmptyIsbn = new Book(\"测试书\", \"测试作者\", \"\");\n    77→            tracker.addBook(bookWithEmptyIsbn);\n    78→        });\n    79→    }\n    80→\n    81→    /**\n    82→     * 测试类型：反例 - 重复添加（覆盖更新）\n    83→     * 输入数据：相同 ISBN 的新图书对象\n    84→     * 预期结果：新图书覆盖旧图书\n    85→     * JUnit 特性：assertAll 分组断言\n    86→     */\n    87→    @Test\n    88→    void addBook_WithDuplicateIsbn_ShouldUpdateExistingBook() {\n    89→        // 准备：先添加一本图书\n    90→        Book originalBook = new Book(\"旧书名\", \"旧作者\", \"ISBN-001\");\n    91→        tracker.addBook(originalBook);\n    92→        assertEquals(1, tracker.getBookCount(), \"初始应该只有1本书\");\n    93→\n    94→        // 执行：添加相同 ISBN 的新图书\n    95→        Book newBook = new Book(\"新书名\", \"新作者\", \"ISBN-001\");\n    96→        tracker.addBook(newBook);\n    97→\n    98→        // 验证：使用 assertAll 进行分组断言\n    99→        assertAll(\"重复添加应覆盖更新\",\n   100→            () -> assertEquals(1, tracker.getBookCount(), \"图书总数应保持为1\"),\n   101→            () -> {\n   102→                Book found = tracker.findByIsbn(\"ISBN-001\");\n   103→                assertNotNull(found);\n   104→                assertEquals(\"新书名\", found.getTitle(), \"书名应被更新\");\n   105→                assertEquals(\"新作者\", found.getAuthor(), \"作者应被更新\");\n   106→            }\n   107→        );\n   108→    }\n   109→\n   110→    // ==================== findByIsbn 测试 ====================\n   111→\n   112→    /**\n   113→     * 测试类型：正例\n   114→     * 输入数据：存在的 ISBN\n   115→     * 预期结果：返回对应的图书对象\n   116→     * JUnit 特性：基本断言\n   117→     */\n   118→    @Test\n   119→    void findByIsbn_WithExistingIsbn_ShouldReturnBook() {\n   120→        // 准备\n   121→        tracker.addBook(testBook);\n   122→\n   123→        // 执行\n   124→        Book found = tracker.findByIsbn(\"978-111\");\n   125→\n   126→        // 验证\n   127→        assertNotNull(found);\n   128→        assertEquals(\"Java 核心技术\", found.getTitle());\n   129→    }\n   130→\n   131→    /**\n   132→     * 测试类型：边界 - 不存在的 ISBN\n   133→     * 输入数据：不存在的 ISBN\n   134→     * 预期结果：返回 null\n   135→     * JUnit 特性：assertNull\n   136→     */\n   137→    @Test\n   138→    void findByIsbn_WithNonExistentIsbn_ShouldReturnNull() {\n   139→        // 执行\n   140→        Book found = tracker.findByIsbn(\"NOT-EXIST\");\n   141→\n   142→        // 验证\n   143→        assertNull(found, \"不存在的 ISBN 应该返回 null\");\n   144→    }\n   145→\n   146→    /**\n   147→     * 测试类型：边界 - null 输入\n   148→     * 输入数据：null\n   149→     * 预期结果：抛出 IllegalArgumentException\n   150→     * JUnit 特性：assertThrows\n   151→     */\n   152→    @Test\n   153→    void findByIsbn_WithNullIsbn_ShouldThrowException() {\n   154→        Exception exception = assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   155→            tracker.findByIsbn(null);\n   156→        });\n   157→        assertEquals(\"ISBN 不能为 null\", exception.getMessage());\n   158→    }\n   159→\n   160→    // ==================== borrowBook 测试 ====================\n   161→\n   162→    /**\n   163→     * 测试类型：正例\n   164→     * 输入数据：存在的 ISBN 和有效借阅人\n   165→     * 预期结果：图书被标记为已借出，借阅记录正确\n   166→     * JUnit 特性：assertTrue, assertEquals\n   167→     */\n   168→    @Test\n   169→    void borrowBook_WithValidInput_ShouldBorrowSuccessfully() {\n   170→        // 准备\n   171→        tracker.addBook(testBook);\n   172→\n   173→        // 执行\n   174→        tracker.borrowBook(\"978-111\", \"小北\");\n   175→\n   176→        // 验证\n   177→        Book found = tracker.findByIsbn(\"978-111\");\n   178→        assertTrue(found.isBorrowed(), \"图书应被标记为已借出\");\n   179→        assertEquals(\"小北\", found.getBorrower(), \"借阅人应正确记录\");\n   180→        assertTrue(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"978-111\", \"小北\"), \"应有借阅记录\");\n   181→    }\n   182→\n   183→    /**\n   184→     * 测试类型：边界 - 图书不存在\n   185→     * 输入数据：不存在的 ISBN\n   186→     * 预期结果：抛出 IllegalArgumentException\n   187→     * JUnit 特性：assertThrows, 验证异常消息\n   188→     */\n   189→    @Test\n   190→    void borrowBook_WithNonExistentBook_ShouldThrowException() {\n   191→        Exception exception = assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   192→            tracker.borrowBook(\"NOT-EXIST\", \"小北\");\n   193→        });\n   194→        assertTrue(exception.getMessage().contains(\"图书不存在\"));\n   195→    }\n   196→\n   197→    /**\n   198→     * 测试类型：边界 - 借阅人为空\n   199→     * 输入数据：空借阅人\n   200→     * 预期结果：抛出 IllegalArgumentException\n   201→     * JUnit 特性：@ParameterizedTest + @NullAndEmptySource 批量测试\n   202→     */\n   203→    @ParameterizedTest\n   204→    @NullAndEmptySource\n   205→    @ValueSource(strings = {\"   \", \"\\t\", \"\\n\"})\n   206→    void borrowBook_WithEmptyBorrower_ShouldThrowException(String invalidBorrower) {\n   207→        // 准备\n   208→        tracker.addBook(testBook);\n   209→\n   210→        // 验证\n   211→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   212→            tracker.borrowBook(\"978-111\", invalidBorrower);\n   213→        });\n   214→    }\n   215→\n   216→    /**\n   217→     * 测试类型：边界 - 图书已被借出\n   218→     * 输入数据：已借出图书的 ISBN\n   219→     * 预期结果：抛出 IllegalArgumentException\n   220→     * JUnit 特性：assertThrows\n   221→     */\n   222→    @Test\n   223→    void borrowBook_WithAlreadyBorrowedBook_ShouldThrowException() {\n   224→        // 准备\n   225→        tracker.addBook(testBook);\n   226→        tracker.borrowBook(\"978-111\", \"小北\");\n   227→\n   228→        // 验证\n   229→        Exception exception = assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   230→            tracker.borrowBook(\"978-111\", \"阿码\");\n   231→        });\n   232→        assertTrue(exception.getMessage().contains(\"已被借出\"));\n   233→    }\n   234→\n   235→    /**\n   236→     * 测试类型：边界 - 无效 ISBN 格式（参数化测试）\n   237→     * 输入数据：多种无效 ISBN\n   238→     * 预期结果：抛出 IllegalArgumentException\n   239→     * JUnit 特性：@ParameterizedTest + @ValueSource 批量测试\n   240→     */\n   241→    @ParameterizedTest\n   242→    @ValueSource(strings = {\"\", \"   \", \"\\t\"})\n   243→    void borrowBook_WithInvalidIsbn_ShouldThrowException(String invalidIsbn) {\n   244→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   245→            tracker.borrowBook(invalidIsbn, \"小北\");\n   246→        });\n   247→    }\n   248→\n   249→    // ==================== returnBook 测试 ====================\n   250→\n   251→    /**\n   252→     * 测试类型：正例\n   253→     * 输入数据：已借出图书的正确 ISBN 和借阅人\n   254→     * 预期结果：图书被标记为未借出，借阅记录清除\n   255→     * JUnit 特性：assertFalse, assertNull\n   256→     */\n   257→    @Test\n   258→    void returnBook_WithValidInput_ShouldReturnSuccessfully() {\n   259→        // 准备\n   260→        tracker.addBook(testBook);\n   261→        tracker.borrowBook(\"978-111\", \"小北\");\n   262→        assertTrue(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"978-111\", \"小北\"));\n   263→\n   264→        // 执行\n   265→        tracker.returnBook(\"978-111\", \"小北\");\n   266→\n   267→        // 验证\n   268→        Book found = tracker.findByIsbn(\"978-111\");\n   269→        assertFalse(found.isBorrowed(), \"图书应被标记为未借出\");\n   270→        assertNull(found.getBorrower(), \"借阅人应被清除\");\n   271→        assertFalse(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"978-111\", \"小北\"), \"借阅记录应被清除\");\n   272→    }\n   273→\n   274→    /**\n   275→     * 测试类型：边界 - 图书未被借出\n   276→     * 输入数据：在架图书的 ISBN\n   277→     * 预期结果：抛出 IllegalArgumentException\n   278→     * JUnit 特性：assertThrows\n   279→     */\n   280→    @Test\n   281→    void returnBook_WithNotBorrowedBook_ShouldThrowException() {\n   282→        // 准备\n   283→        tracker.addBook(testBook);\n   284→\n   285→        // 验证\n   286→        Exception exception = assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   287→            tracker.returnBook(\"978-111\", \"小北\");\n   288→        });\n   289→        assertTrue(exception.getMessage().contains(\"未被借出\"));\n   290→    }\n   291→\n   292→    /**\n   293→     * 测试类型：边界 - 错误的借阅人\n   294→     * 输入数据：正确的 ISBN 但错误的借阅人\n   295→     * 预期结果：抛出 IllegalArgumentException\n   296→     * JUnit 特性：assertThrows, 验证异常消息包含预期内容\n   297→     */\n   298→    @Test\n   299→    void returnBook_WithWrongBorrower_ShouldThrowException() {\n   300→        // 准备\n   301→        tracker.addBook(testBook);\n   302→        tracker.borrowBook(\"978-111\", \"小北\");\n   303→\n   304→        // 验证\n   305→        Exception exception = assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   306→            tracker.returnBook(\"978-111\", \"阿码\");\n   307→        });\n   308→        assertTrue(exception.getMessage().contains(\"借阅人不符\"));\n   309→    }\n   310→\n   311→    /**\n   312→     * 测试类型：边界 - 图书不存在\n   313→     * 输入数据：不存在的 ISBN\n   314→     * 预期结果：抛出 IllegalArgumentException\n   315→     * JUnit 特性：assertThrows\n   316→     */\n   317→    @Test\n   318→    void returnBook_WithNonExistentBook_ShouldThrowException() {\n   319→        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> {\n   320→            tracker.returnBook(\"NOT-EXIST\", \"小北\");\n   321→        });\n   322→    }\n   323→\n   324→    // ==================== 参数化批量测试 ====================\n   325→\n   326→    /**\n   327→     * 测试类型：正例/边界（批量）\n   328→     * 输入数据：多组借阅场景\n   329→     * 预期结果：hasBorrowRecord 返回正确值\n   330→     * JUnit 特性：@ParameterizedTest + @CsvSource\n   331→     */\n   332→    @ParameterizedTest(name = \"ISBN={0}, 借阅人={1}, 预期存在={2}\")\n   333→    @CsvSource({\n   334→        \"ISBN-1, 小北, true\",     // 正常借阅记录\n   335→        \"ISBN-1, 阿码, false\",    // 书存在但借给其他人\n   336→        \"ISBN-2, 小北, false\",    // 书不存在\n   337→        \"ISBN-1, '', false\"       // 空借阅人\n   338→    })\n   339→    void hasBorrowRecord_WithVariousScenarios_ShouldReturnCorrectResult(\n   340→            String isbn, String borrower, boolean expectedExists) {\n   341→        // 准备\n   342→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书1\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   343→        tracker.borrowBook(\"ISBN-1\", \"小北\");\n   344→\n   345→        // 执行\n   346→        boolean exists = tracker.hasBorrowRecord(isbn, borrower);\n   347→\n   348→        // 验证\n   349→        assertEquals(expectedExists, exists,\n   350→            String.format(\"ISBN=%s, 借阅人=%s 的预期结果应为 %b\", isbn, borrower, expectedExists));\n   351→    }\n   352→\n   353→    // ==================== 附加方法测试（提升覆盖率）====================\n   354→\n   355→    /**\n   356→     * 测试 listAllBooks 方法\n   357→     * JUnit 特性：assertEquals\n   358→     */\n   359→    @Test\n   360→    void listAllBooks_WithMultipleBooks_ShouldReturnAllBooks() {\n   361→        // 准备\n   362→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书1\", \"作者A\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   363→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书2\", \"作者B\", \"ISBN-2\"));\n   364→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书3\", \"作者C\", \"ISBN-3\"));\n   365→\n   366→        // 执行\n   367→        var books = tracker.listAllBooks();\n   368→\n   369→        // 验证\n   370→        assertEquals(3, books.size(), \"应返回所有图书\");\n   371→    }\n   372→\n   373→    /**\n   374→     * 测试 removeBook 方法 - 成功移除\n   375→     */\n   376→    @Test\n   377→    void removeBook_WithExistingBook_ShouldRemoveSuccessfully() {\n   378→        // 准备\n   379→        tracker.addBook(testBook);\n   380→        assertNotNull(tracker.findByIsbn(\"978-111\"));\n   381→\n   382→        // 执行\n   383→        boolean removed = tracker.removeBook(\"978-111\");\n   384→\n   385→        // 验证\n   386→        assertTrue(removed, \"应成功移除\");\n   387→        assertNull(tracker.findByIsbn(\"978-111\"), \"移除后应找不到\");\n   388→    }\n   389→\n   390→    /**\n   391→     * 测试 removeBook 方法 - 移除不存在的书\n   392→     */\n   393→    @Test\n   394→    void removeBook_WithNonExistentBook_ShouldReturnFalse() {\n   395→        boolean removed = tracker.removeBook(\"NOT-EXIST\");\n   396→        assertFalse(removed, \"移除不存在的书应返回 false\");\n   397→    }\n   398→\n   399→    /**\n   400→     * 测试 removeBook 方法 - null 输入\n   401→     */\n   402→    @Test\n   403→    void removeBook_WithNullIsbn_ShouldReturnFalse() {\n   404→        boolean removed = tracker.removeBook(null);\n   405→        assertFalse(removed, \"null ISBN 应返回 false\");\n   406→    }\n   407→\n   408→    /**\n   409→     * 测试 getBookCount 方法\n   410→     */\n   411→    @Test\n   412→    void getBookCount_ShouldReturnCorrectCount() {\n   413→        assertEquals(0, tracker.getBookCount(), \"初始应为 0\");\n   414→\n   415→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书1\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-1\"));\n   416→        assertEquals(1, tracker.getBookCount());\n   417→\n   418→        tracker.addBook(new Book(\"书2\", \"作者\", \"ISBN-2\"));\n   419→        assertEquals(2, tracker.getBookCount());\n   420→\n   421→        tracker.removeBook(\"ISBN-1\");\n   422→        assertEquals(1, tracker.getBookCount());\n   423→    }\n   424→\n   425→    /**\n   426→     * 完整借阅流程测试\n   427→     * JUnit 特性：assertAll 进行多维度验证\n   428→     */\n   429→    @Test\n   430→    void fullBorrowAndReturnCycle_ShouldWorkCorrectly() {\n   431→        // 准备\n   432→        Book book = new Book(\"设计模式\", \"GoF\", \"ISBN-DP\");\n   433→        tracker.addBook(book);\n   434→\n   435→        // 执行：借阅流程\n   436→        tracker.borrowBook(\"ISBN-DP\", \"小北\");\n   437→\n   438→        // 验证：借阅状态\n   439→        assertAll(\"借阅后状态验证\",\n   440→            () -> assertTrue(tracker.findByIsbn(\"ISBN-DP\").isBorrowed()),\n   441→            () -> assertEquals(\"小北\", tracker.findByIsbn(\"ISBN-DP\").getBorrower()),\n   442→            () -> assertTrue(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"ISBN-DP\", \"小北\"))\n   443→        );\n   444→\n   445→        // 执行：归还流程\n   446→        tracker.returnBook(\"ISBN-DP\", \"小北\");\n   447→\n   448→        // 验证：归还状态\n   449→        assertAll(\"归还后状态验证\",\n   450→            () -> assertFalse(tracker.findByIsbn(\"ISBN-DP\").isBorrowed()),\n   451→            () -> assertNull(tracker.findByIsbn(\"ISBN-DP\").getBorrower()),\n   452→            () -> assertFalse(tracker.hasBorrowRecord(\"ISBN-DP\", \"小北\"))\n   453→        );\n   454→    }\n   455→}\n   456→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_14f9c3afc6df478fbe525d70","session_id":"5071dd61-4cb8-490e-a97a-6edea443d84b","uuid":"107f5f67-cfa0-45c9-96f6-38ce586c7a90"}
