{"type":"stream_event","event":{"type":"content_block_delta","index":1,"delta":{"type":"input_json_delta","partial_json":"{\"command\":\"git add chapters/week_06/ANCHORS.yml chapters/week_06/ASSIGNMENT.md chapters/week_06/CHAPTER.md chapters/week_06/QA_REPORT.md chapters/week_06/RUBRIC.md chapters/week_06/examples/02_first_test.java chapters/week_06/examples/05_parameterized_test.java && git commit -m \\\"$(cat <<'EOF'\\nfix(week_06): 修复 QA S1-S4 问题 + 叙事质量提升\\n\\n技术问题修复：\\n- S1: 修复 @ValueSource + @NullAndEmptySource 重复测试用例\\n- S2: 添加 World Quality Report 参考链接\\n- S2: ASSIGNMENT 异常类型与实现一致 (IllegalArgumentException)\\n- S2: 修复示例代码 Task ID → Book ISBN 复制粘贴错误\\n- S2: CHAPTER 方法名 findBook → findByIsbn 与 starter_code 一致\\n- S3: 更新 ANCHORS.yml AI 专栏 verification 字段\\n- S3: 添加 borrower 参数校验到 02_first_test.java\\n- S3: RUBRIC.md 明确 AI 协作为可选附加分\\n- S4: 改进第2节叙事流程\\n\\n叙事质量提升：\\n- 第5节开篇增加阿码追问\\\"为什么不写循环\\\"场景\\n- 小结改为叙述段落，增加画面感\\n- Definition of Done 拆分为三组\\n\\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\\nEOF\\n)\\\"\",\"description\":\"Commit week_06 QA fixes\"}"}},"session_id":"5071dd61-4cb8-490e-a97a-6edea443d84b","parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"ce6e5e5f-7bef-4372-8a48-38fd37d2a144"}
